(85, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1740321438382_obefawby0mi.mp3', 'compressed_1740321438382_obefawby0mi.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1740321438382_obefawby0mi.mp4', 'Hi, I\'m Gauri, currently pursuing my mba, Johnson School of Business. I have excited to share my journey with you. From my school days, I have been an active participant in various competitions and events. This experience helped me to build confidence, teamwork and leadership skills. Early on in college, I took on the responsibility of managing festivals and competitions, further strengthening my skills in event planning, problem solving and communication. I always eager to learn and explore new opportunities. I have attended workshop on Capital Markets, Trading and Technology for the future, an international conference on Digital transformation in Banking and Finance, a national conference on Technopionership. This experience had dependent my understanding of finance and technologies and entrepreneurship beyond academics. I love drawing. It is my way to express and relax and express creativity. I always open to learning, growing and taking on new challenges. Thank you for watching.', 45, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1740321438382_obefawby0mi.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1740321438382_obefawby0mi.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[0.01415418740361929,-0.01007470116019249,-0.016722412779927254,0.03651700168848038,0.09089589864015579,0.053822387009859085,0.012801659293472767,0.03623001277446747,0.012065020389854908,0.008720745332539082,-0.0400167815387249,0.017467593774199486,-0.04020553082227707,0.02694564126431942,-0.012632381170988083,0.04844179376959801,0.05719985067844391,0.017514904960989952,0.02166392281651497,-0.010229409672319889,0.007923290133476257,0.08135214447975159,0.04964045062661171,0.052481044083833694,0.05112481489777565,0.0242498479783535,0.04224096238613129,0.012679150328040123,-