(86, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1740326048147_0dy7gkcyxizk.mp3', 'compressed_1740326048147_0dy7gkcyxizk.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1740326048147_0dy7gkcyxizk.mp4', 'Hey there. I\'m Monica Jain, an MBA student specializing in finance at Jadson School of Business. Here\'s something interesting. In 2021, I started to learn about investing just out of curiosity. And I found myself getting deeper into financial markets, wealth management. And that\'s when I realized finance was where I wanted to be. My experience as a senior systems engineer for almost two years helped me to build my problem solving skills. But I wanted to develop my expertise in finance. And that\'s why I did a certification on financial planning from cfi, which gave me a better understanding about the field. I\'ve also completed a job simulation by JP Morgan on investment banking and I enjoy working with numbers and data. So what sets me apart? I bring a mix of both technical expertise and financial knowledge which bridges the gap between both technology and finance. So if you\'re looking for someone who can connect the dots, let\'s connect. Thank you.', 43, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1740326048147_0dy7gkcyxizk.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1740326048147_0dy7gkcyxizk.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[0.021694013848900795,-0.024443846195936203,0.0034776884131133556,0.05642841383814812,0.1089901253581047,0.05167451873421669,0.0122127840295434,0.028900250792503357,0.011541741900146008,-0.003479184815660119,-0.01578708551824093,0.039238475263118744,-0.01344032771885395,0.015887293964624405,-0.01367255114018917,0.04266208037734032,0.059244442731142044,0.015828214585781097,0.019687781110405922,-0.004301819950342178,-0.007915569469332695,0.06349506974220276,0.05587683245539665,0.034876760095357895,0.03300965949892998,0.02884206734597683,0.020128726959228516,-0.0056203557178378105,-0.023027842864394