(144, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1743181010033_wyy7kfn9anp.mp3', 'compressed_1743181010033_wyy7kfn9anp.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1743181010033_wyy7kfn9anp.mp4', 'Hello, I\'m S. Samen, pursuing my Bachelor\'s in Technology in Computer Science here at Vit vellore. I\'m a third year student and a two time merit scholarship recipient with a CGPA of 9.46. My interests include in the field of artificial intelligence, LLMs and data analytics and to support my interest in these fields I have done a couple of courses in Coursera and Udemy. My projects include a Plant Disease Classifier which analyzes and categorizes the diseases in plants in a wide variety of thousand categories. I used OpenCV and TensorFlow for this project. Another project of mine is called Vitality plus and is a medical prescription analyzer. It analyzes the prescriptions of patients and directly integrates it to their Google Calendar so that they can get automated reminders on when to take their medicines. And I have done a couple of data analytics projects as well. I am very eager for further interaction from you and you can have a hold of me through my LinkedIn profile which I have attached to my resume. Thank you for your time.', 72, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1743181010033_wyy7kfn9anp.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1743181010033_wyy7kfn9anp.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[0.04417607560753822,7.050397689454257E-4,-0.016801223158836365,0.037620335817337036,0.10218852758407593,0.07189985364675522,-0.0040060183964669704,0.034933388233184814,0.01606294885277748,-0.007646629586815834,-0.01922040618956089,0.027038993313908577,-0.030339378863573074,0.02398061566054821,0.009433644823729992,0.06426407396793365,0.07868418097496033,0.021416861563920975,0.026855943724513054,0.017373839393258095,0.015615864656865597,0.06985189020633698,0.04697883501648903,0.046125978231430054,0.020747877657413483,0.01