(158, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1743851537083_42n1f7yzai2.mp3', 'compressed_1743851537083_42n1f7yzai2.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1743851537083_42n1f7yzai2.mp4', 'Hi, I have just completed my MBA in HR because of my natural pull towards people and systems. I also am a keen writer where I write poems and stories and this has shaped how I communicate, how I can express myself clearly and connect with people. I love combining different domains and topics to find unique solutions. For example, I use the DMACC process from Six Sigma to solve a recruitment bottleneck and I have an HR blog page on which I update my learnings and my perspective weekly. I also have a keen interest in industrial relationships which was born due to my summer internship at Mondelez International where I worked with the shop floor employees and this would help me use my negotiation skills. My biggest strength lies in connecting people, processes and taking action towards this. Thank you.', 76, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1743851537083_42n1f7yzai2.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1743851537083_42n1f7yzai2.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[0.019772229716181755,0.02098359353840351,-0.0075966184958815575,0.046569373458623886,0.10337885469198227,0.05545790120959282,0.01579711213707924,0.01954512856900692,0.024510232731699944,-0.002586072077974677,-0.030898287892341614,0.022103343158960342,-0.029774585738778114,0.024209817871451378,-0.006728040520101786,0.042915936559438705,0.055263929069042206,0.017277654260396957,0.010242418386042118,-0.014495354145765305,0.0069981906563043594,0.06328193098306656,0.04305436834692955,0.03733566403388977,0.05647188797593117,0.022901851683855057,0.0414101704955101,0.008222509175539017,-0.026812588796019554,0.033195625990629196,0.026465538889169693,-0.03304430842399597,0.020143043249845505,0.01020544208586216,0.01960437186062336,-0.010987027548253536,0.0126772867