(163, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1744119949313_rf5v4vw58nl.mp3', 'compressed_1744119949313_rf5v4vw58nl.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744119949313_rf5v4vw58nl.mp4', 'Hi, I am Mike. I have always been curious why people choose one brand over another and that\'s what pulled me into marketing. I enjoy mixing creativity with logic, whether it\'s building a campaign or doing research. I love finding smart and simple ways to connect with people. I am good at sporting pattern, so just give me some data and I\'ll tell you story from it. I am someone who loves working with teams, trying new things and learning on the go. When I\'m not working, I love playing badminton and cooking for my family. I\'m excited to bring some fresh new ideas and positive energy wherever I work.', 88, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744119949313_rf5v4vw58nl.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1744119949313_rf5v4vw58nl.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[0.023205364122986794,0.020402781665325165,-5.765127134509385E-4,0.05076323077082634,0.09118104726076126,0.05352114140987396,0.005530396476387978,0.04601242020726204,0.03205891698598862,-0.009452068246901035,-0.03442209213972092,0.01747955195605755,-0.033704131841659546,0.005773303564637899,-0.012326262891292572,0.054096076637506485,0.05071447044610977,0.04860033839941025,0.02212860994040966,0.01818668842315674,-0.005044951103627682,0.06937120109796524,0.027945315465331078,0.04771529510617256,0.05929193273186684,0.013174399733543396,0.03315548598766327,0.01649264618754387,-0.05337592214345932,0.025885527953505516,0.024936145171523094,-0.012276267632842064,0.028731219470500946,0.0027411403134465218,0.010142340324819088,-0.028768494725227356,0.02746248058974743,0.029982874169945717,0.004844294395297766,0.011335186660289764,-0.07626630365848541,0.03710700199007988,-0.004525580443441868,-0.016360357403755188,-0.04490944370627403,0.018635528162121773,-0.0342