(164, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1744123375163_ab0v5te7p4s.mp3', 'compressed_1744123375163_ab0v5te7p4s.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744123375163_ab0v5te7p4s.mp4', 'Hi, I am Tanisha, a recent MBA graduate from IFMR with a specialization in Finance. During my mba, I have worked on several academic projects, valuing companies like Warren Beverages Titan to analyzing one of the India\'s biggest banking frauds, EBG Shipyard to create risk modelling project, building a loan amortization schedule. Each experience has deepened my understanding with a real world financial systems and decision making. I strongly believe in continuous learning, which is why I pursued certifications in Power, bi, Corporate Finance and Excel to stay updated with the tools and techniques needed in today\'s corporate world. Beyond academics, I\'ve been a Campus Ambassador, core member of HR Committee and Photography Club and actively involved in Youth Empowerment Initiative. These roles have helped me grow as a team player and an effective communicator. Thank you.', 87, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744123375163_ab0v5te7p4s.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1744123375163_ab0v5te7p4s.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[0.01846141926944256,-0.015543962828814983,-0.014339466579258442,0.041478998959064484,0.09547633677721024,0.0554606094956398,0.01447593979537487,0.025844551622867584,0.007401306182146072,0.005486701149493456,-0.03127852827310562,0.02841135486960411,-0.02076682262122631,0.019255010411143303,0.002923758700489998,0.04760514199733734,0.08112215250730515,0.018784407526254654,0.014573482796549797,-0.008224014192819595,0.0043757883831858635,0.07634378224611282,0.052219588309526443,0.03648509457707405,0.047040458768606186,0.03348691016435623,0.0338699109852314,0.009381656534969807,-0.027666935697197914,0.01118561439216137,0.03425828740000725,-0.02126704342663288,0.017500828951597214,0.02253