(165, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1744157300346_wzn3d6qrbvn.mp3', 'compressed_1744157300346_wzn3d6qrbvn.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744157300346_wzn3d6qrbvn.mp4', 'Hi, I\'m Harinath, a MBA graduate majored in Quantitative Finance from IFMR Graduate School of Business. Out of my own interest I did credit risk analysis for Peugeot Automobile company who was planning to set up their electric vehicle plant in India. Here I analyzed their financials, credit scores and ESG metrics in order to have a basic idea about the organization. And I also did stress testing to analyze how company performs in adverse conditions. And I did risk modeling by taking all the risk they can face after setting up a plant in India and model them in order to give a quantitative output. By analyzing all this I found out the credit worthiness of the organization. Apart from this, I was the Innovation and Entrepreneurship Cell coordinator for my department where we brainstorm and ideate solutions for various problem statements and I did my summer internship in Mondelez International as Supply Chain Management intern, I do food blogging in my free time and I\'m searching for job opportunities in finance, risk and consulting domain. Thank you.', 82, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744157300346_wzn3d6qrbvn.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1744157300346_wzn3d6qrbvn.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[0.02226327732205391,0.010494720190763474,-0.017196638509631157,0.04368981346487999,0.10577674210071564,0.06077204644680023,-0.005847861524671316,0.038332629948854446,0.01340561918914318,0.0033485284075140953,-0.021348990499973297,0.020017776638269424,-0.028882838785648346,0.017167426645755768,-0.007360420655459166,0.056452639400959015,0.062071751803159714,0.02333967015147209,0.018274381756782532,-0.009233621880412102,0.015146085992455482,0.08372662961483002,0.054269079118967056,0.03972301259636879,0.047