(170, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1744269232647_z2070tgxn3g.mp3', 'compressed_1744269232647_z2070tgxn3g.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744269232647_z2070tgxn3g.mp4', 'Hi, I\'m Debjit Das. I recently completed my MBA in Finance from IFMR Graduate School of Business and I did my BCom from St Xavier\'s University. During my MBA, I did a live project with Finlatics on equity markets where I handled a virtual portfolio and I had to research stocks based on the data and market trends. I did my internship from Ekarup where I had to backtest trading strategies and during my internship I created a strategy that had a 72% winning probability and it was later implemented on the firm\'s marketplace. Apart from this, I helped in organizing our cultural fest called Abyudaya where I saw end to end execution of the flagship event \"The Last One Standing\". During my academic journey, I\'ve acquired skills in financial analysis, Excel, data interpretation and capital markets and I\'m currently looking for opportunities in the finance domain and I hope to keep learning and growing. Thank you.', 79, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744269232647_z2070tgxn3g.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1744269232647_z2070tgxn3g.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[0.010262061841785908,-0.0151393823325634,-0.005293603520840406,0.04625410586595535,0.10077811032533646,0.05281207337975502,0.005532366223633289,0.02908579260110855,0.01140185073018074,-6.381301209330559E-4,-0.032742615789175034,0.01841850019991398,-0.030530739575624466,0.015878796577453613,0.007507528178393841,0.04365941882133484,0.07484623044729233,0.0040785884484648705,0.021196398884058,-0.007739882450550795,0.002616558689624071,0.06931623071432114,0.0453316792845726,0.051227204501628876,0.046283964067697525,0.0360167920589447,0.03621416911482811,0.009848702698946,-0.0332164540886879,0.011764847673475742,0.03774558752775192,-0.0053151897154