(171, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1744270621998_p9ov6s5027g.mp3', 'compressed_1744270621998_p9ov6s5027g.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744270621998_p9ov6s5027g.mp4', 'Hi, my name is Shruti Nair and I\'m a fresh MBA graduate specialized in finance from IFMR GSB Krea University with hands on exposure to market risk and data analytics. My strength lies in applying financial theories to real world scenarios through live projects. I conducted a credit risk evaluation using bank loan data where I tackled data inconsistencies and identified high risk applicant profiles. This helped improve default prediction accuracy by 70%, directly supporting Safer loan approvals. I also implemented a short Iron Condor strategy in Tata Motors analyzing nifty wicks to optimize returns under low volatility. Another key project involved the forensic analysis of the 22,000 crore ABG shipyard fraud where I pinpointed governance lapses and suggested preventive controls. Combined with my internship at Paterson securities pvt ltd. where I applied var, conditional VAR and backtested strategies, I bring a strong risk mindset, analytical rigor and a drive to deliver data backed insights. Thank you.', 93, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744270621998_p9ov6s5027g.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1744270621998_p9ov6s5027g.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[0.024798445403575897,-0.023522721603512764,-0.001859426498413086,0.051886968314647675,0.10062199085950851,0.06436697393655777,-0.006516074296087027,0.017332838848233223,0.01455063745379448,-0.007966013625264168,-0.01384711917489767,0.024626106023788452,-0.026368070393800735,0.015810055658221245,0.0022380345035344362,0.043428026139736176,0.07372715324163437,0.008324657566845417,0.01446186751127243,-0.009883769787847996,0.005849314387887716,0.08058219403028488,0.04386264085769653,0.036021944135427475,0.030378304421901703,0.03291057050228119,0.0301783531