(177, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1744287680334_maz86p3wud.mp3', 'compressed_1744287680334_maz86p3wud.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744287680334_maz86p3wud.mp4', 'Hi, I am Nachiketa Bhargujar, currently pursuing my MBA at IFMR with the specialization in Finance. I come from agriculture background, Having completed my BSc in Agriculture with distinction, which gives me a unique perspective on data discipline and problem solving. At ifmr, I have worked on diverse academic projects from analyzing banking frauds and credit risk to using Power, BI and SQL for business performance analysis. One of my key experience was a caption stimulation where I led strategy across marketing, HR and operations to win the highest market share among 10 companies. During my internship, I analyzed over 200 derivative contracts and developed integrated futures and option strategies that reduced volatility by 25% and boosted returns. Beyond academics, I am active member of the QuizLab, a tracker and national NCC credit and I\'m excited to apply this in dynamic finance and business strategy. Role.', 97, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744287680334_maz86p3wud.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1744287680334_maz86p3wud.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[0.024227067828178406,-0.01757831871509552,-0.007102450355887413,0.04523850232362747,0.10276435315608978,0.048944760113954544,0.0018253695452585816,0.031551968306303024,-0.0020159189589321613,0.017693471163511276,-0.03435575217008591,0.02735353261232376,-0.022902710363268852,0.02428225241601467,0.00239936844445765,0.058998048305511475,0.08087578415870667,0.012142378836870193,0.017705563455820084,-0.011332415975630283,0.00386093114502728,0.06324638426303864,0.06251996755599976,0.03505370020866394,0.049837611615657806,0.031459614634513855,0.02865925431251526,0.01901227980852127,-0.03883800655603409,0.024223720654845238,0.04297775775194168,-0.02271130