(180, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1744291234712_80h5cejl57d.mp3', 'compressed_1744291234712_80h5cejl57d.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744291234712_80h5cejl57d.mp4', 'Hi everyone, My name is Sumit Kumar Sahoo. I started my career as junior Engineer at Corrosion Protection Private Limited where I worked on improving the production efficiency, reducing the lead time and managing more than 50 clients. There I developed strong analytical and client management skill. However, my growing interest in finance has led me to transition into this field. During my MBA I worked on different project. First I valued GCPL company using different financial methodologies like APV, DCF, WACC. Besides that I have created an investment portfolio using Markowitz Portfolio theory balancing both risk and return across different sectors. I have recently interned at Nalco under the guidance of Mr. Jyotiranjan Mohanty where I learnt how NALCO has been managing his working capital despite having large scale of import and export and remain debt free for years.', 104, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744291234712_80h5cejl57d.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1744291234712_80h5cejl57d.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[0.023356547579169273,-0.006648487877100706,-0.0018610019469633698,0.04084878787398338,0.10554797947406769,0.06484203785657883,-0.00855229888111353,0.03346283733844757,0.011380763724446297,0.0030441952403634787,-0.016897033900022507,0.033132653683423996,-0.03758355975151062,0.026559732854366302,0.013047176413238049,0.051309484988451004,0.07082167267799377,0.009306039661169052,0.03116573393344879,0.014776043593883514,0.00758792320266366,0.0777399092912674,0.06440486013889313,0.042282868176698685,0.046174827963113785,0.03237214684486389,0.015778858214616776,0.014935649931430817,-0.03747263178229332,0.01432905811816454,0.04376506060361862,-0.006993925664573908,0.007679229136556387,0.00527