(184, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1744294990337_aym9xjjsoiu.mp3', 'compressed_1744294990337_aym9xjjsoiu.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744294990337_aym9xjjsoiu.mp4', 'Hi, I\'m Poorva Rathore an MBA graduate from IFMR GSB with a strong interest in risk management. I have explored credit and operational risk through my coursework and projects, using tools like Excel, Power BI and Python to support data driven decision making. I have won business valuation competition at IMT Hyderabad and secured 4th rank in IIM Calcutta\'s product decode. I have also completed few certifications in financial modeling and risk management to strengthen my technical foundation. As a summer intern, I worked on credit assessment and portfolio monitoring, gaining practical exposure to financial risk analysis. I was also a core member of IFMR GSB\'s speakers club. I\'m equally interested in business valuation and consulting roles. Thank you.', 99, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744294990337_aym9xjjsoiu.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1744294990337_aym9xjjsoiu.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[0.028098179027438164,-0.012240812182426453,-5.349341663531959E-4,0.03957327827811241,0.10504152625799179,0.05239085108041763,0.0017526678275316954,0.019960975274443626,0.011407854966819286,0.015093325637280941,-0.026840301230549812,0.036373887211084366,-0.028366129845380783,0.025382025167346,-0.004677502438426018,0.05849549546837807,0.06579503417015076,0.007960379123687744,0.0031258140224963427,-0.0063153719529509544,0.017856040969491005,0.08159210532903671,0.058260731399059296,0.04090256989002228,0.04781290888786316,0.0385008305311203,0.034295473247766495,0.020119626075029373,-0.03322794660925865,0.006020605564117432,0.04582224413752556,-0.026788437739014626,0.013298286125063896,0.024966761469841003,0.02784973941743374,-9.168651304207742E-4,0.0021742405369877815,0.03300957381725311,0.0050575388595461