(187, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1744295990519_mt5nyojkloh.mp3', 'compressed_1744295990519_mt5nyojkloh.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744295990519_mt5nyojkloh.mp4', 'My name is Yashi Te and I come from Kolkata. I started my career with computer science, but somewhere down the line I always was intrigued by the finance world and how it works and how numbers can tell a different story. That\'s when I decided to pursue MBA and I joined IFMR gsb. Apart from this, I have also done my internship in Patterson Securities Private Limited as a derivative and market risk intern wherein I gained theoretical knowledge on derivative markets and the financial world. Apart from my academics, I always was keen in giving it back to the Society and hence I was a part of the Rotaract Club of Calcutta Samaritans during my undergraduate days and after joining IFMR I was a part of the Samarthan Committee of the college which is the CSR committee and apart from this I am also a keen dancer.', 131, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744295990519_mt5nyojkloh.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1744295990519_mt5nyojkloh.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[0.03127278387546539,-0.018315816298127174,-0.002386000007390976,0.04371580109000206,0.09055528789758682,0.061751481145620346,0.002012518933042884,0.03472496569156647,0.014653180725872517,0.004407878965139389,-0.035339124500751495,0.02192322351038456,-0.027001099660992622,0.028676657006144524,0.004344241693615913,0.04720240831375122,0.08173128217458725,0.009059328585863113,0.0033617299050092697,-0.009892333298921585,0.0132780522108078,0.09081418067216873,0.04802253097295761,0.04366845637559891,0.035616517066955566,0.039690710604190826,0.027882244437932968,0.019985966384410858,-0.03369392454624176,0.016998814418911934,0.04008946940302849,-0.011413907632231712,0.007910446263849735,0.02595343254506588,0.009032945148646832,-0.02098758891224861,0.0053673