(188, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1744296752606_wx6m1iip5t.mp3', 'compressed_1744296752606_wx6m1iip5t.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744296752606_wx6m1iip5t.mp4', 'Hello, I am Shilpa Karmakar, an MBA graduate from IFMR GSB Krea University. So I do have knowledge about Python, RStudio and Power BI. I can even do the technical analysis using Python. And I worked on a multiple financial projects during my academics which includes valuation project on sun pharmaceutical industry, ratio analysis of bosch to analyze the financial health of the company, portfolio optimization by calculating estimated shortfall and VAR to assess the risk associated within the portfolio. I have also worked on a simulated pitchbook. So talking about my internship,so I was a part of Paterson Securities Private Limited where I was a derivative intern and my work is to analyze the strategies based on the market condition and I\'m also a part of CSR committee of IFMR gsb. Thank you.', 78, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744296752606_wx6m1iip5t.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1744296752606_wx6m1iip5t.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[0.029526209458708763,-0.014633437618613243,-0.013054106384515762,0.044054433703422546,0.09637876600027084,0.04673243686556816,0.00233857287093997,0.025780119001865387,0.019512509927153587,0.008169448003172874,-0.022960269823670387,0.009434817358851433,-0.03212808072566986,0.026112107560038567,3.175028832629323E-4,0.05446978285908699,0.07101204991340637,0.008283422328531742,0.008139406330883503,0.0026793689467012882,0.015060734003782272,0.09278953075408936,0.04098890721797943,0.031519815325737,0.0380307175219059,0.029069865122437477,0.030418695881962776,0.01733875274658203,-0.03420274704694748,0.013720374554395676,0.038813699036836624,-0.016714569181203842,7.81217881012708E-4,0.013087047263979912,0.03147384524345398,-0.008116534911096096,0.002899240469560027,0.0466996