(189, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1744297108007_s7xn4k1p0to.mp3', 'compressed_1744297108007_s7xn4k1p0to.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744297108007_s7xn4k1p0to.mp4', 'Hi, I\'m Ishika Saraogi. I have currently completed my MBA from IFIMA GSE with the focus on Finance and Risk management. I hold a BA in English and bring unique blend of communication and analytical skills to the people. I am certified in Certified in Equity, Derivative Risk Management, Ms. Excel and Power bi. I\'ve also worked on machine learning models to predict credit default and performed in in depth financial analysis and business valuation using multiple methodologies. I interned at Partisan securities where I focused on derivative strategies, option trading and risk management using tool like Opstra and Sensible. I also interned at Anglo Packaging Private Limited after graduation which gave me hands on experience, exposure to business, corporations and corporate workflow. From participating in Tata Imagination Challenge to winning a business pitch competition, I thrive on solving real world problems. I am now looking for opportunities to grow as a financial analyst and a strategist. Let\'s connect.', 127, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744297108007_s7xn4k1p0to.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1744297108007_s7xn4k1p0to.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[0.016707248985767365,-0.026535889133810997,-0.009639563970267773,0.039258018136024475,0.09793935716152191,0.061525121331214905,0.001399707281962037,0.02689816802740097,0.012020346708595753,0.0024823485873639584,-0.02379911206662655,0.025934750214219093,-0.014584838412702084,0.020391978323459625,-0.01336362399160862,0.049357373267412186,0.06782106310129166,0.01632053405046463,0.011082179844379425,-0.023744741454720497,0.00997099094092846,0.08136747777462006,0.04195668175816536,0.027509840205311775,0.04279104247689247,0.034724246710538864,0.0301885