(190, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1744298070455_xcal7ab6ta8.mp3', 'compressed_1744298070455_xcal7ab6ta8.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744298070455_xcal7ab6ta8.mp4', 'I believe stories are everywhere, be it people, places, experiences, or even numbers. I just completed my MBA in Finance specialization from ifmr, but I\'ve always been a storyteller and writer at heart. I interned in Peterson securities and Equity Derivatives and Market Research where I combined strategy, data research. I also have exposure to machine learning, Python, SQL and marketing concepts. I don\'t want to limit myself to a box. I feel my growth lies in exposure to different domains. Apart from this, I also represented a club at ifmr. It\'s a theatre club. From past two years I\'ve been writing scripts, coordinating within the team departments, collaborating, negotiating for budgets, costumes just to put in a show and sell a story to the audience. And I Hope in past 60 seconds I could sell my story to you. Thank you.', 116, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744298070455_xcal7ab6ta8.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1744298070455_xcal7ab6ta8.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[0.017797119915485382,0.00407634349539876,8.536665700376034E-4,0.055063966661691666,0.10039883852005005,0.03860773146152496,0.010468491353094578,0.037809018045663834,0.010805727913975716,0.007464156951755285,-0.019262278452515602,0.039211761206388474,-0.023514313623309135,0.026853682473301888,-0.016934644430875778,0.047188952565193176,0.045560337603092194,0.005489889066666365,0.015108193270862103,-0.01280941441655159,-6.585186929441988E-4,0.0663471668958664,0.046427566558122635,0.053929004818201065,0.04128536209464073,0.018494978547096252,0.018322361633181572,0.012024518102407455,-0.03009013459086418,0.028143202885985374,0.023069310933351517,-0.029806705191731453,0.007845464162528515,-9.48413617152255E-6,0.009881115518510342,-0.