(191, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1744299519373_wx4epmjdemk.mp3', 'compressed_1744299519373_wx4epmjdemk.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744299519373_wx4epmjdemk.mp4', 'Hello, My name is George M Kolethu. I am recently passed out of IFMR GSB with MBA degree in finance. Over the past few years I have built a strong foundation in operations and finance. Moreover, I have work experience with a company called Startek in Bangalore and MRF tyres and as a part of my MBA curriculum, recently I did my internship in a company called Accendon Technologies where I got an opportunity to work on the financial modeling, industry analysis and budgeting which sparked a deep interest in the credit analysis. So I am particularly drawn on how these credit analysts evaluate the financial risk profile of a company. So my aspiration is to grow as a credit analyst where I could use my analytical skills and industry knowledge. Thank you.', 122, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744299519373_wx4epmjdemk.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1744299519373_wx4epmjdemk.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[0.022631937637925148,0.00680737616494298,-0.008234010078012943,0.03906700387597084,0.10841488093137741,0.05591161549091339,-0.00405646488070488,0.03000585548579693,0.009923013858497143,0.0025617610663175583,-0.03771144896745682,0.028486469760537148,-0.03287506103515625,0.01377381943166256,0.004721036646515131,0.04854651540517807,0.06702649593353271,0.020546525716781616,0.018071603029966354,-0.00921214371919632,0.0013774029212072492,0.08680728077888489,0.053841523826122284,0.037023670971393585,0.044320348650217056,0.041766226291656494,0.030750133097171783,0.01726154424250126,-0.03901016712188721,0.015560932457447052,0.04044785350561142,-0.006164242513477802,0.016920555382966995,0.012744342908263206,0.01888306997716427,-0.010279051028192043,0.012913728132843971,0.03266843035817146,0.014174802228808403,0.017