(192, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1744299483655_9q7jyfhoipn.mp3', 'compressed_1744299483655_9q7jyfhoipn.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744299483655_9q7jyfhoipn.mp4', 'Hello everyone. My name is Tamana Nadlani. I belong to a business class family. So from the initial days only, I was too much involved in knowing how a business entity runs. So to dive deep into it, I decided to pursue MBA in Finance from ifmr. I have completed my sixth semester from ifmr. I did my internship at Ekuru in Coimbatore as a research associate where there we learned various derivative strategies and we learned various valuation techniques because there are different valuation techniques for different types of firms. I have done a project as a credit risk analyst for RJ Enterprises. It was a poultry farm business. There we decided whether to grant them loan based on their loan to value ratio and their collateral. I have done a portfolio management project also. There we decided which portfolio is the best based on the mean, standard deviation and sort in a ratio. Thank you.', 106, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744299483655_9q7jyfhoipn.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1744299483655_9q7jyfhoipn.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[0.02691376768052578,-0.010956144891679287,-0.014777748845517635,0.02729363553225994,0.10526921600103378,0.0682995393872261,0.004374349024146795,0.02600785903632641,0.00996626727283001,0.010853933170437813,-0.02168979123234749,0.02288874238729477,-0.019628794863820076,0.018763959407806396,0.002813027473166585,0.051422953605651855,0.06657668948173523,0.01288439892232418,0.02206643670797348,-9.003751911222935E-4,0.007607531733810902,0.07327599823474884,0.05077807232737541,0.03700849413871765,0.0400322824716568,0.02871369756758213,0.036855682730674744,0.025654977187514305,-0.03513573482632637,0.004018182400614023,0.04082894325256348,-0.02465997450053692,0.0171571187674999