(193, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1744300042259_nyakqpgxlfb.mp3', 'compressed_1744300042259_nyakqpgxlfb.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744300042259_nyakqpgxlfb.mp4', 'Hello, My name is Yash Nair. I am born and brought up in Mumbai. I have completed my BBA in International Business from Dybattil School of Management in Navi Mumbai Post which I decided to join IFMR GSB to pursue my MBA in Finance as I was interested in finance to equip myself with more knowledge and skills in the BFSI sector, I have done certification certification like NISM Equity Derivatives to get more knowledge about equity and derivatives market. Last summer I got an opportunity to intern at Mavericks Business and Market Research where I learned how to analyze a company and an industry as a whole. In second year of my MBA I learned subjects like derivatives valuation, mergers and acquisitions, investment banking, etc where I where I got an aspiration to build a career in private equity, investment banking or other risk related fields. Thank you.', 130, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744300042259_nyakqpgxlfb.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1744300042259_nyakqpgxlfb.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[0.020242631435394287,-0.012149710208177567,0.006905387155711651,0.037880901247262955,0.10045258700847626,0.05132023245096207,0.010184453800320625,0.02440086007118225,0.015434026718139648,0.0062594106420874596,-0.03549378737807274,0.02119889110326767,-0.026289792731404305,0.032338034361600876,0.015159298665821552,0.05770113319158554,0.07608171552419662,0.006183176301419735,-0.002683310303837061,-0.004070871509611607,0.010292266495525837,0.07996822893619537,0.05504803732037544,0.04516422003507614,0.03880772367119789,0.035143088549375534,0.029438920319080353,0.031801480799913406,-0.03996136039495468,0.014882508665323257,0.032252002507448196,-0.025825658813118935,0.009223670698702335,0.03437905013561249,0