(194, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1744300494042_4fx1okzuvtq.mp3', 'compressed_1744300494042_4fx1okzuvtq.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744300494042_4fx1okzuvtq.mp4', 'Hello, I\'m Moshi Kumari, a marketing enthusiast with a strong interest in communications strategy and data driven storytelling. I\'m currently pursuing my MBA in Marketing at IFMR GSB where I have had the opportunity to work on exciting projects. One of them was Explore Chennai where I created and managed a website, implemented SEO strategies and used social media to increase our reach, achieving over 16,000 impressions in just three months. During my summer internship at Easter Society, I worked on a large scale outreach campaign across 13 states, identifying and onboarding over 50ambassadors using tools like Excel, Tableau and QCUP for data and project management. I also serve as the Public Relations Representative at my institute where I plan communication strategies and handle external engagement. I am now looking for a role where I can bring my energy, curiosity and marketing skills to real world business challenges. Thank you.', 124, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744300494042_4fx1okzuvtq.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1744300494042_4fx1okzuvtq.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[0.01140227448195219,-0.014224555343389511,0.007228679955005646,0.045512862503528595,0.09243317693471909,0.05406814441084862,0.014118057675659657,0.034732893109321594,0.019473470747470856,0.007934624329209328,-0.04329325631260872,0.017868896946310997,-0.0295991413295269,0.019920052960515022,-0.0011973605724051595,0.055189333856105804,0.06688308715820312,0.024579502642154694,0.020679639652371407,-0.007869629189372063,0.01627446711063385,0.0856115072965622,0.041737742722034454,0.03723297640681267,0.04819725453853607,0.008070386946201324,0.036978885531425476,0.009396939538419247,-0.03913944214582443,0.0017638485878705978,0