(196, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1744302562360_man8smgf63p.mp3', 'compressed_1744302562360_man8smgf63p.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744302562360_man8smgf63p.mp4', 'Hello everyone. I am currently pursuing my MBA at ASMAR Graduate School of Business with a strong focus on finance. I hold a BCom degree from Himalayan Garwal University where I developed a deep interest in financial analysis and valuation. I also did several certifications including Microsoft Excel, Power BI Busting and Forecasting and Traded Modeling. I have got hands on experience with financial projects such as conducting the valuation of Marico limited using various financial models like dcf, Relative Valuation and apb. Additionally, I have analyzed Varun Beverage\'s financial performance through detailed ratio analysis and decomposed Roe using DuPont analysis. I also did a credit proposal and risk analysis of poultry business. My internship at Maverick Business and Market Research as a research analyst allowed me to further refine my skills in market analysis, competitive positioning and financial research. I worked on creating industry and company profiles and delivered actionable strategies in such.', 107, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744302562360_man8smgf63p.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1744302562360_man8smgf63p.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[0.0212341770529747,7.016253075562418E-4,-0.018350932747125626,0.03534070402383804,0.10059036314487457,0.062194641679525375,0.0035343568306416273,0.025230318307876587,0.009080160409212112,0.0049587213434278965,-0.034296270459890366,0.02800939418375492,-0.0268618892878294,0.021112360060214996,0.00587677164003253,0.05687842145562172,0.06977355480194092,0.019034666940569878,0.02845071628689766,-0.017352452501654625,0.004989138804376125,0.06711854040622711,0.044681113213300705,0.03661090508103371,0.04117059335112572,0.027808720245957375,0.03695662319