(198, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1744303327977_ncpb1tu314m.mp3', 'compressed_1744303327977_ncpb1tu314m.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744303327977_ncpb1tu314m.mp4', 'Hello, My name is Shruti Jain, currently pursuing MBA from IFR Graduate School of Business with a strong focus on capital market risk management and banking regulation. I have gained and hands on experience through an internship in Derivatives and Risk management where I have explored about equity derivatives, various option strategies and worked on platforms like OXTRA and Sensibilities. Additionally, as a part of my target projects, I did financial modeling and valuation at analysis of growth ridge consumers and a strategic risk evaluation and global stock indices to deepen my knowledge on portfolio management and financial markets. Now I am looking forward to apply my analytical skills and a passion for finance to roles in credit risk valuation and capital and liquidity management. Thanks for watching.', 125, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744303327977_ncpb1tu314m.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1744303327977_ncpb1tu314m.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[0.027760330587625504,-0.0030654098372906446,-0.00611624913290143,0.04093501344323158,0.09800931811332703,0.05200522020459175,-8.396422490477562E-4,0.03137149661779404,0.006904138717800379,0.006628113333135843,-0.0207444429397583,0.035295452922582626,-0.027051489800214767,0.018212774768471718,0.009265451692044735,0.04513293132185936,0.06186923384666443,0.006687115412205458,0.004168163053691387,-0.013559904880821705,0.002577492967247963,0.07240944355726242,0.0437813438475132,0.04158749058842659,0.037358157336711884,0.029065171256661415,0.027799103409051895,0.022112809121608734,-0.030320245772600174,0.008620372042059898,0.03532307967543602,-0.008134102448821068,0.0077304476872086525,0.017953386530280113,0.011084216646850109,0.007173772435635328,0.005