(200, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1744305784186_rr9f8bahexg.mp3', 'compressed_1744305784186_rr9f8bahexg.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744305784186_rr9f8bahexg.mp4', 'Hello, I\'m Meloni from Udaipur, Rajasthan. I completed my MBA in Finance and while graduating I qualified for two levels of Chartered Accountancy course. My article should give me exposure to auditing, taxation and financial compliance. Pursuing an MBA helped me bridge my accounting foundation with strategic thinking. During my coursework, I valued Tata Motors using various models as Assess credit risk for a startup using Bayesian norms Analyze global indices using simulations. During my internship, I worked on SAP software for vendor and fund management to streamline the reporting process. As a fresher, I\'m open to diverse roles across the finance sector including credit risk, treasury consulting, etc where I can learn continuously and hone my skills. Thank you.', 108, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744305784186_rr9f8bahexg.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1744305784186_rr9f8bahexg.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[0.012867409735918045,-0.001020530005916953,-0.010543137788772583,0.038730185478925705,0.09635627269744873,0.054949551820755005,0.022032268345355988,0.029571810737252235,0.00429018959403038,0.006451649125665426,-0.026427671313285828,0.03038177639245987,-0.024374965578317642,0.00369616923853755,-0.0013568546855822206,0.046186596155166626,0.06346265971660614,0.01110032293945551,0.01894332468509674,-0.020307930186390877,0.005922951269894838,0.08200620114803314,0.056527987122535706,0.048649419099092484,0.0431942343711853,0.0322590097784996,0.04030213877558708,0.012085785157978535,-0.03306089714169502,0.010943066328763962,0.03535400703549385,-0.008103160187602043,0.014776771888136864,0.026980914175510406,0.021656343713402748,-0.00272108125500381,0.012077638879418373,0.035438887774944305,0.0086