(201, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1744306084519_oddoeix2vfe.mp3', 'compressed_1744306084519_oddoeix2vfe.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744306084519_oddoeix2vfe.mp4', 'Hello, my name is Hrithika and I recently completed my MBA from IFMAR Graduate School of Business. Prior to that, I did my BCom from Lucknow University, graduating in 2021. During my undergraduation, I was an active member of the Cultural Committee and coordinated several college events. I also interned at the Buzz Paper as a Digital Marketing intern. Post undergraduation, I joined my uncle\'s retail clothing business where I worked for two years handling sales and operations and got hands on experience in customer relations. For the summer internship, I interned at Patterson securities as a Brand manager and over the past two years of my mba I worked around market research, product management, SQL and Power BI projects. Coming to my strength. I am a quick learner, adaptable and comfortable, working both independently and in teams. I enjoy taking ownership of tasks and I\'m known for being detailed, oriented and reliable. Thank you.', 119, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744306084519_oddoeix2vfe.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1744306084519_oddoeix2vfe.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[0.024266349151730537,-0.007382016163319349,-4.367224173620343E-4,0.03227372467517853,0.09916401654481888,0.058709487318992615,0.005300768651068211,0.02766493149101734,0.012630920857191086,0.02142161875963211,-0.03584766387939453,0.01453681942075491,-0.02888079360127449,0.014995675534009933,0.0027507864870131016,0.0496056005358696,0.07146083563566208,0.02557787299156189,0.019803127273917198,-0.011075974442064762,0.02225576713681221,0.07854897528886795,0.04997862130403519,0.039558518677949905,0.05445593222975731,0.02568943426012993,0.045416586101055145,0.008452007547020912,-0.03251056745648384,0.015719294548034668,0.03494