(206, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1744310614583_2e5yq9ghue2.mp3', 'compressed_1744310614583_2e5yq9ghue2.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744310614583_2e5yq9ghue2.mp4', 'Some people read numbers, I read their story behind them. Hello, I\'m Archi walia, someone with a strong foundation in commerce, real world experience at Accenture and a growing expertise in finance and valuation through my MBA journey At Accenture, I didn\'t just process invoices, I handled global reconciliations work across ERP platforms and ensured process ran smoothly and accurately. That experience taught me that finance is not just precision, it\'s accountability. Over time I\'ve developed a deep interest in financial analysis and valuation. I\'ve built models like dcf, FCFF and Relative valuation, applying them to companies like Colgate Palmolive to understand where real value lies. What sets me apart is how I think, with logic, curiosity and structure. I like simplifying complexity, spotting patterns and bringing clarity to decisions outside finance. I find calm in creating and organizing. For me, attention to detail isn\'t just a task, it\'s a mindset. I don\'t just work with numbers, I work with purpose. Thank you.', 129, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744310614583_2e5yq9ghue2.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1744310614583_2e5yq9ghue2.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[0.013050174340605736,-0.007949382066726685,0.006608380004763603,0.04611087217926979,0.10094819962978363,0.06671169400215149,8.0916314618662E-4,0.029945410788059235,0.017620285972952843,-0.008380945771932602,-0.015845200046896935,0.026903828606009483,-0.032109614461660385,0.013731072656810284,-0.007102085743099451,0.057082295417785645,0.06413207203149796,0.014247147366404533,0.03291989117860794,-0.01942216046154499,7.071881555020809E-4,0.07415177673101425,0.03582848981022835,0.031611692160367966,0.038643524050712585,0.0262236054