(209, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1744311698802_8owbz00lnzb.mp3', 'compressed_1744311698802_8owbz00lnzb.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744311698802_8owbz00lnzb.mp4', 'Hi, I\'m Ashwin Pillai, a Quantitative Finance major@ifmr GSB with a deep interest in applying mathematical and statistical models to solve real world financial problems. From interning at Crisil, where I worked on credit risk analysis, to my M and A experience at Singhi Advisors, I\'ve consistently honed my analytical and research skills. I\'ve also tackled projects ranging from portfolio optimization to econometric modeling and derivative strategy skills I believe are central to modern finance. I\'m not just about numbers. I lead on and off the field as the captain of my undergrad college football team and a Grade one pianist from the Trinity College of Music, London. I\'ve also played volleyball at the district level and actively volunteer for animal NGOs. If you\'re looking for someone who blends finance, creativity and leadership with passion and purpose, I am your guy.', 95, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744311698802_8owbz00lnzb.mp4', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[0.009993556886911392,-0.007563337683677673,-0.013540499843657017,0.04772625491023064,0.09041845053434372,0.0597723014652729,-0.005166976246982813,0.025553429499268532,0.00541670061647892,-0.007940704934298992,-0.017414534464478493,0.01760760322213173,-0.030942663550376892,0.0162773709744215,8.781118667684495E-4,0.0536498986184597,0.06483601033687592,0.01049793604761362,0.011750372126698494,-0.015884988009929657,0.017413945868611336,0.08533058315515518,0.05068708583712578,0.040400419384241104,0.02915194444358349,0.022515468299388885,0.025844264775514603,0.013503770343959332,-0.02971487306058407,0.017034195363521576,0.053408585488796234,-9.529644739814103E-5,0.012962181121110916,0.014726205728948116,0.01981501467525959,-0.019741682335734367,0.01794174127280712,0.03510364