(211, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1744312468027_h420eqq989a.mp3', 'compressed_1744312468027_h420eqq989a.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744312468027_h420eqq989a.mp4', 'Hi, my name is Ronak Jain, a finance enthusiast who\'s cleared Sienta Group 1, interned at a strategy consulting firm and started a new product line for my family business, all before completing mba. So recently I completed my MBA in Finance from IFMR Graduate School of Business, KRA University. During my summer internship, I interned at KRG Strategy, Consulted Private Limited where I did market research, financial modeling and business valuation. I also hold certifications in Equity derivatives, Excel, vba, Power BI and Bloomberg Market Concepts. I also analyze various derivative trading strategies and build financial models for companies like Varun Beverages. Right now, I\'m looking for an opportunity in financial analysis, financial modeling, business valuation, risk domain where I can combine my technical skills to bring together smart financial decision. So if you\'re looking for a person who can bring together financial skills and business acumen, let\'s connect. Thank you.', 121, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744312468027_h420eqq989a.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1744312468027_h420eqq989a.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[0.023096896708011627,-0.0043212901800870895,-5.479308892972767E-4,0.05199749022722244,0.1071319431066513,0.04515187069773674,-5.131545476615429E-4,0.029680438339710236,0.00840033683925867,-0.0049480265006423,-0.020924413576722145,0.023958418518304825,-0.015121780335903168,0.025056645274162292,-0.004007408861070871,0.05705059692263603,0.06603560596704483,0.016675837337970734,0.026309406384825706,-0.0159160066395998,0.0011007863795384765,0.06662267446517944,0.046617768704891205,0.04029577970504761,0.03739127889275551,0.03035254217684269,0.022854354232549667,0.010120372287929