(213, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1744364163319_9a408bin4h.mp3', 'compressed_1744364163319_9a408bin4h.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744364163319_9a408bin4h.mp4', 'Hello, I am Aditya Patnaik. I recently completed my MBA in Finance from IFMA GSB where I developed knowledge in financial modeling, valuation, equity research along with other finance concepts. Before this, I earned my BBA from Utkal University where I developed strong grasp of business and financial analysis. During my mba, I led many key projects like building a five year financial model for Titan company to forecast its growth and access its market value. To strengthen my skills, I earned certification in NISM Equity Derivatives Research Analyst along with Excel and Power bi. I interned as a wealth management trainee at Impetus Arthasudra where I gained knowledge of various asset classes. Here I performed investor profiling, risk assessment, analyzed Indian energy sector and prepared an equity research report on Oil India Ltd. Combining my academic background, technical certification and hands on experience, I am eager to contribute to the roles that require analytical skills and strategic decision making. Thank you.', 113, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744364163319_9a408bin4h.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1744364163319_9a408bin4h.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[0.016279414296150208,-0.015343636274337769,-0.014935526065528393,0.0490947850048542,0.08961006999015808,0.05597720667719841,0.005653835833072662,0.035120364278554916,0.008992691524326801,0.007539113983511925,-0.023294929414987564,0.020663782954216003,-0.025985850021243095,0.01966105028986931,0.009233100339770317,0.057526055723428726,0.06674936413764954,0.006608583498746157,0.007316645700484514,-0.0021172636188566685,0.013606060296297073,0.07475169003009796,0.06129167228937149,0.03589029610157013,0.04367360472679138,0.025960611179471016,0