(215, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1744697297186_6prdusyiibl.mp3', 'compressed_1744697297186_6prdusyiibl.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744697297186_6prdusyiibl.mp4', 'Hi there, My name is Anmol Khan Dhalia. Just completed my MBA from IFMA Graduate School of Business, Korea University with the focus on Finance and Data Science. Prior to this, I have completed my Computer Science Engineering from Presidency University, Bangalore. To further enhance my finance skills, I recently passed CFA Level 1 and did my internship with Patterson securities as a Derivatives and market risk intern. My primary goal was to automate strategies that included straddles and triangles. Apart from it, I have also built few algorithmic strategies based on Pine Editor and backtested them on Python. My tools and technology stack includes Python, SQL, Power, BI and Machine learning deep learning models. Apart from it, I\'m also In addition to my academics, I\'m also into fitness and nutrition and I have been following a structured five day routine from last five years. So that\'s all about me. Thank you so much for listening.', 92, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1744697297186_6prdusyiibl.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1744697297186_6prdusyiibl.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[0.01652747206389904,-0.009830576367676258,-0.00588013231754303,0.047876354306936264,0.10118693858385086,0.05503656715154648,-8.502719720127061E-5,0.02496102638542652,0.01889592781662941,-0.008681833744049072,-0.028622863814234734,0.02742503583431244,-0.03477342799305916,0.01435357891023159,0.012378151528537273,0.044940441846847534,0.07487796992063522,0.004137508571147919,0.01827368512749672,-0.0018906592158600688,-0.0015020485734567046,0.06677140295505524,0.04195890575647354,0.03741073235869408,0.025405270978808403,0.028725624084472656,0.0187542587518692,0.0060770693235099316,-0.03201250731945038,0.029805893078446388,0.