(218, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1745648163609_c6qqcbmgxyr.mp3', 'compressed_1745648163609_c6qqcbmgxyr.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1745648163609_c6qqcbmgxyr.mp4', 'Hi, I\'m Vinod Kumar, currently pursuing my MBA in Finance from PSC Institute of Management. I have completed my undergraduation in BCOM Professional Accounting and I also have a two months internship experience at Chola Mandalam Investment and Finance company where I was working as a credit intern under the Loan against Property segment. During my internship I have conducted a creditworthiness assessment for over 15 plus applicants and led the underwriting process for loan amount rupees 75 lakh of loan proposal. And I also have gained experience in credit analysis and financial evaluation of customers by analyzing the financial statements, credit reports and collateral documents of the properties pledged. And I also have hands on experience in Excel, Power, BI and Tableau. That\'s all. Thank you.', 137, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1745648163609_c6qqcbmgxyr.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1745648163609_c6qqcbmgxyr.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[0.02023063413798809,-0.018313981592655182,0.010227617807686329,0.04011324420571327,0.10126228630542755,0.07003428041934967,-0.0026512197218835354,0.02702252008020878,0.0018632134888321161,-0.0020957610104233027,-0.027777215465903282,0.02349654585123062,-0.026325391605496407,0.016110597178339958,0.02026592567563057,0.062245674431324005,0.07980550825595856,0.02031811885535717,0.03279642015695572,-0.023381797596812248,0.026598619297146797,0.08736903220415115,0.05620686337351799,0.030068518593907356,0.035459574311971664,0.03488115221261978,0.02062990888953209,0.002794747008010745,-0.04225282371044159,0.01004519872367382,0.04094098135828972,-0.013176322914659977,0.0036648563109338284,0.012462550774216652,0.018537871539592743,-0.016386553645133972,0.01702686026