(227, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1745656167038_nytmywq5kfn.mp3', 'compressed_1745656167038_nytmywq5kfn.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1745656167038_nytmywq5kfn.mp4', 'Hi, I am Monica D. I\'ve completed my MBA in Finance from PSGIM and hold a certification in Research Analysis. I\'ve interned in the mutual fund industry where I conducted market research to support business decisions. I enjoy backend operations, stakeholder engagement, and simplifying complex data into actionable strategies. As a part of my academic projects, I worked on a momentum and volatility-based stock study using the Nifty 500, applying indicators such as Sharpe Ratio, Martin Ratio, Ulcer Index, and standard deviation to build an active fund portfolio. I am proficient with Excel, Word and PowerPoint and I have a strong grasp of project evaluation metrics such as NPV, IRR, Payback period and so on. Passionate about fintech, research and stakeholder engagement, I am excited to take on challenges, grow with a purpose, and make real impact in the industry.', 142, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1745656167038_nytmywq5kfn.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1745656167038_nytmywq5kfn.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[0.020662931725382805,-0.03586939722299576,-0.003247947199270129,0.059140194207429886,0.10196197032928467,0.05679849162697792,-4.50385530712083E-4,0.025195838883519173,0.006582276429980993,0.003178683342412114,-0.016936572268605232,0.017044687643647194,-0.013068722561001778,0.013009401969611645,-0.008646217174828053,0.04787582531571388,0.06738822907209396,0.012085143476724625,0.013503032736480236,-0.011692098341882229,0.003970746416598558,0.06589995324611664,0.05526522919535637,0.03785964101552963,0.043356020003557205,0.03176850825548172,0.047410596162080765,-0.01104746200144291,-0.023643547669053078,0.020686553791165352,0.0376746840775013,-0.007701804395765066,0.01965620368719101,0.0242659579