(228, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1745658134045_whvuy101prn.mp3', 'compressed_1745658134045_whvuy101prn.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1745658134045_whvuy101prn.mp4', 'Greetings sir. Thank you for giving me this opportunity to introduce myself. I\'m Dashni from Prichirapalli. I did my undergrad in Commerce at Cauvery College and I\'m currently pursuing my MBA at PSG by a strong passion in finance and sales. I did my internship at LG Rubber as a financial analyst intern where I had gained a hands on experience on the financial analysis and understanding on the real world applications. I pride myself to be a self motivated individual where I handle situations in a better way effectively and I do multitasking also. Beyond economics. I enjoy immersing myself into the art of cooking, doing Mehendi designs and reading novels. I have secured various prices for doing mehandir designs during my handheld. I co founded and started Happy Events and business specializing in event organizing with my friends. That\'s all about me sir. Thank you.', 148, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1745658134045_whvuy101prn.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1745658134045_whvuy101prn.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[0.017536738887429237,0.0016539901262149215,-0.007734266575425863,0.03886498138308525,0.09934470802545547,0.07462876290082932,-0.008242561481893063,0.033704306930303574,0.006428368855267763,-0.013217879459261894,-0.0275788065046072,0.007963785901665688,-0.03949766606092453,0.017497636377811432,0.011061024852097034,0.0560176782310009,0.07212623208761215,0.019099844619631767,0.013285872526466846,-0.004627022426575422,0.014823241159319878,0.0779634639620781,0.04448557645082474,0.040012650191783905,0.038097258657217026,0.03495324030518532,0.02710185945034027,0.017676202580332756,-0.04309004545211792,0.010156391188502312,0.03969233110547066,-0.014392728917300701,0.02394530363380909,0.00368206