(242, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1748589575123_34ayrtyrry.mp3', 'compressed_1748589575123_34ayrtyrry.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1748589575123_34ayrtyrry.mp4', 'Hi there. I am Shobhika from Tirupu. I recently completed my MBA with specialization in finance at Janssen School of Business, Coimbatore. I completed my summer internship with the Stock Holding Corporation of India at Coimbatore where I gained valuable insights about the functioning of the capital market and also about the operational side of the securities management. Additionally, I improved my communication skills through client interaction and gained exposure to the digital platforms. This experience deeply deepened my interest in the financial market and enhanced me practical understanding about the investment opportunities. Apart from my studies, I hold certification in Tally prime with GST Mutual Fundation from nism. I am excited about the opportunity to discuss how my skills will benefit your team. Thank you.', 157, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1748589575123_34ayrtyrry.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1748589575123_34ayrtyrry.jpg', '2025-05-30 12:54:07.814871', NULL, NULL, NULL, '[0.013917419128119946,-0.02164013311266899,-0.00250157224945724,0.03550804406404495,0.1041373685002327,0.06175318732857704,9.780419059097767E-4,0.025113658979535103,0.0135496249422431,0.007115481421351433,-0.016262086108326912,0.023212457075715065,-0.030992822721600533,0.017494436353445053,0.01657937839627266,0.049191929399967194,0.07110165059566498,0.012927043251693249,0.019155090674757957,-0.0034592377487570047,0.010424785315990448,0.07408703863620758,0.054672274738550186,0.04596693441271782,0.042843353003263474,0.033428359776735306,0.03306790068745613,0.01672915555536747,-0.0325847864151001,0.002048033056780696,0.046315256506204605,-0.011526953428983688,0.011470732279121876,0.020202025771141052,0.01298272516578435