(310, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1757398424658.mp3', 'compressed_1757398424658.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1757398424658.mp4', 'Hi. My story is about a journey of growth from a student professional who is not afraid to take risks. It began with my BBA at srm, which laid the foundation for my career and soon after that I stepped into a corporate world at Citibank. I started as a Citipone officer but my determination performance quickly set me apart. In my first year I was awarded the Best new Hiring Agent and also I earned a promotion to City Retention Officer. But I wanted more to explore, learn and expand my horizons and this led me to pursue my masters at MZ\'s Boy Tanden School of Business, where my world truly opened up. I embraced every opportunity from leading students initiative, contributing to campus newsletter and also to participating in NGO activities. It was here I truly discovered my calling marketing and sales. I further honed my skills with Google certification and also a valuable internship at an international retail brand, Tunel Gaia. And my journey is a testament to adaptability, leadership and drive. I\'m a learner team player who brings a unique blend of business acumen and creative marketing expertise and my name is Noah.', 263, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1757398424658.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1757398424658.jpg', '2025-09-09 11:45:31.666998', 'C191', 'null', 'null', '[0.015194009058177471,-0.021792279556393623,-0.00913107767701149,0.036618415266275406,0.09202174842357635,0.06477659195661545,0.0016501897480338812,0.036187801510095596,0.025443382561206818,-0.0020811595022678375,-0.036848220974206924,0.003792390925809741,-0.030020862817764282,0.02169661410152912,0.009421315975487232,0.04060584679245949,0.06905065476894379,0.03497437760233879,0.010071431286633015,-0.012430594302713871,-0.0010012107668444514,0.08429059386253357,0.04