(322, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1757402293788.mp3', 'compressed_1757402293788.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1757402293788.mp4', 'Hello, I\'m Dharani Dharan and I see myself as a passionate marketer in the making. To begin this journey, I am pursuing my PGDM in Marketing at MCC Boyd Tyndall School of Business. I have done two internships, one at MRF Tires as a Sales and marketing intern where I understood how sales and customer insights drive business, and another one at Global Logistics Solution where I analyzed logistics efficiency and trade policies along practical experience. I have strengthened my profile through certification in AI in Marketing, Supply Chain and Digital Marketing. These certifications have helped me to apply technology driven approaches and use data effectively and understand the digital side of modern business. I believe my adaptability and strong teamwork skills allow me to thrive in dynamic environments and collaborate effectively with diverse teams to achieve goals. Thank you for watching.', 245, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1757402293788.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1757402293788.jpg', '2025-09-09 12:48:48.482171', 'C191', 'null', 'null', '[0.015158222988247871,0.0034759712871164083,-0.011573506519198418,0.04958178848028183,0.10584744811058044,0.06409673392772675,-0.009743843227624893,0.032596077769994736,0.01655680499970913,0.0074670519679784775,-0.04319394379854202,0.01610686630010605,-0.037627145648002625,0.02206125296652317,0.01740271784365177,0.060989879071712494,0.07415376603603363,0.021076098084449768,0.013754572719335556,-0.0014961959095671773,0.002241967711597681,0.05398271605372429,0.04370199516415596,0.03803581744432449,0.041992947459220886,0.012285551987588406,0.036390163004398346,0.03327331319451332,-0.0394536629319191,0.018486296758055687,0.027162058278918266,-0.038320839405059814,0.01969839632511139,0.0228227060288