(324, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1757402237155.mp3', 'compressed_1757402237155.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1757402237155.mp4', 'Hello, My name is Ashwin Kumavi and I am pursuing my PGDM at MCC POI Tainan School of Business. I recently interned with Prabhuda Silada Private Limited where I studied IPO performance from 2020 to 2025. I analyzed listing gains, returns and market sentiment giving me hands on exposure to equity valuation and capital market dynamics. I also worked with Concerns Universe foundation where I contributed to implementing the NIOS education program called School Dr. Together with my team, we enabled over 100 students to resume their studies and successfully raised 13.6 lakh to expand these initiatives. Through this diverse experience, I have built strong abilities in financial analysis, data visualization and community engagement. I am excited to apply them in dynamic business environment. Thank you.', 243, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1757402237155.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1757402237155.jpg', '2025-09-09 12:54:22.430375', 'C191', 'null', 'null', '[0.0069876620545983315,-0.012463212013244629,-0.022410912439227104,0.04374552518129349,0.09493661671876907,0.06588172167539597,-0.005809465888887644,0.03205715864896774,0.007331048604100943,0.0032706339843571186,-0.025944164022803307,0.011044399812817574,-0.03386864811182022,0.02590351551771164,0.010494044050574303,0.04621907323598862,0.06595731526613235,0.007007608190178871,0.013096745125949383,0.005576285533607006,0.008612986654043198,0.07210948318243027,0.0424661859869957,0.03911316767334938,0.027928154915571213,0.019960058853030205,0.026278018951416016,0.00691071106120944,-0.03470033034682274,-0.002100863493978977,0.03176475316286087,-0.008400251157581806,0.016012003645300865,0.030571261420845985,0.026294229552149773,-0.00815788097679615,0.015989411622285843,0.04307505860924721,0.0091