(326, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1757404027957.mp3', 'compressed_1757404027957.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1757404027957.mp4', 'Hello, My name is Lovit Dharma and I am currently pursuing my second year of PGDM in Marketing at MCG Bioder School of Business. I recently completed my summer internship at SRL UK limited As a Marketing intern, so where I worked on a key project to develop a profit and loss model to evaluate profitability from fuel sales. I also created a sales dashboard to analyze buyer behavior and fuel trends and our final analysis were shared with the sales and marketing team in the UK to guide the future strategies. I am also skilled in Ms. Office power, BI tableau and RStudio and I have also completed a Coursera course on Marketing Research and Consumer Behavior with a strong foundation in marketing, practical internship exposure and industry recognized certification. I believe I have the right mindset and attitude and I am eager to apply my skills, insights and creativity to deliver measurable impact and contribute to your organization\'s growth. Thank you.', 215, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1757404027957.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1757404027957.jpg', '2025-09-09 13:18:28.061585', 'C191', 'null', 'null', '[0.023226022720336914,1.3627407315652817E-4,-0.002445046789944172,0.053431183099746704,0.0946100503206253,0.05744384974241257,-8.300018816953525E-5,0.02015979215502739,0.028345877304673195,0.0088336868211627,-0.019036155194044113,0.01309274323284626,-0.03795964643359184,0.018009500578045845,0.009365895763039589,0.053981054574251175,0.06526969373226166,0.02782296948134899,0.022997088730335236,6.355600780807436E-4,0.01714589260518551,0.06402573734521866,0.042382922023534775,0.0407109260559082,0.04665541276335716,0.02153758704662323,0.03821518272161484,0.013414643704891205,-0.03971428796648979,0.018742943182587624,0.026455994695425034,-0