(342, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1757409767789.mp3', 'compressed_1757409767789.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1757409767789.mp4', 'If I had to sum up myself in onen, I\'d say this I connect people, processes and data to create impact Hi, I\'m Hari Bhaskar Meynan. I\'m pursuing my PGDM in HR and analytics at MCC Boyton School of Business. Along the way I\'ve gained hands on HR experience at RANA steering Systems, managing end to end recruitment, building standard operating procedures to streamline HR processes, and turning LMS data into insights that make training programs stronger. Outside the classroom. I lead the placement committee driving corporate engagement and I\'ve also collaborated with an organization, xnora, on sustainability projects, an experience that taught me the power of teamwork and creative problem solving. But here\'s what really excites me when you think about HR today. Do you see it as more as a strategic partner shaping the business or as a problem solver tackling challenges in real time? That\'s the conversation I want to have and the kind of value I\'m eager to bring to your team. Thank you.', 270, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1757409767789.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1757409767789.jpg', '2025-09-09 14:53:51.206474', 'C191', 'null', 'null', '[0.016262250021100044,0.003019548486918211,-0.0011165954638272524,0.04537404328584671,0.1052393987774849,0.05061318352818489,-0.016917387023568153,0.014041333459317684,0.012202480807900429,-0.003689911449328065,-0.03367738425731659,0.0036770605947822332,-0.024169638752937317,0.0138652753084898,0.003662616480141878,0.036075811833143234,0.07360757142305374,0.0201569851487875,0.013847344554960728,-0.018118754029273987,0.019825538620352745,0.07024531811475754,0.030424177646636963,0.04394735023379326,0.04838711395859718,0.008135237731039524,0.025337133556604385,-0.0036997459828853607,-0.0241470001637