(350, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1757414481293.mp3', 'compressed_1757414481293.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1757414481293.mp4', 'Hi, I am Karthik, currently pursuing my PGDM at MCC Boydton School of Business specializing in finance. With analytics as my minor. I am passionate about turning numbers into strategy and using data to drive smart business decisions. My journey so far includes a short term finance internship at Lincoln Electric where I worked on financial benchmarking and market performance analysis, sharpening my analytical mindset. I also completed my summer internship at Ashok Leilan, one of India\'s leading automotive genes where I contributed to pricing, strategy evaluation, comparative financial analysis and dashboard creation using Power bi, helping transform raw data into actionable insights. Beyond academics, I actively participate in business case competitions and finance clubs which keeps me sharp on real world problem solving. I also enjoy public speaking, fitness and exploring new technologies which help me stay creative and disciplined. This experience has given me a blend of financial acumen, analytical thinking and hands on problem solving skills that I am excited to bring into my next opportunity. My goal is to combine finance, analytics and technology to create value and drive business growth that.', 244, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1757414481293.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1757414481293.jpg', '2025-09-09 16:12:35.661219', 'C191', 'null', 'null', '[0.011000782251358032,-0.018336070701479912,-0.014246846549212933,0.056441616266965866,0.10675571113824844,0.06352263689041138,-0.0028279272373765707,0.037094954401254654,0.026407919824123383,-0.0012152873678132892,-0.017741184681653976,0.008457782678306103,-0.023425700142979622,0.012513453140854836,0.0055252076126635075,0.05311699956655502,0.07044325023889542,0.020021043717861176,0.