(352, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1757414783467.mp3', 'compressed_1757414783467.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1757414783467.mp4', 'Hi, I\'m Joshua. My story began with a passion for understanding how business handle money, which led me to study Commerce at Mendez Christian College. There I grew not just academically but also as a leader serving as a class representative. Today I am pursuing my PGDM in finance where I have built strong analytics skills. During my internship at MRF Ltd. I worked on real world problems like bills, payable trends, cash flows and taxation. To diversify, I explored FMCG with Unibrik and community work with Plastic for Change. Beyond academics, sports, music and scouts have shaped me into a disciplined team player who adapts quickly and take initiative. Thank you.', 234, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1757414783467.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1757414783467.jpg', '2025-09-09 16:18:50.114895', 'C191', 'null', 'null', '[0.024916397407650948,-0.011095994152128696,-0.005103327799588442,0.053590692579746246,0.0898432731628418,0.0761938989162445,-6.812356295995414E-4,0.035929467529058456,0.014937157742679119,-0.009678378701210022,-0.014783436432480812,0.014534014277160168,-0.03105621039867401,0.01708630658686161,-0.007885480299592018,0.04916208237409592,0.07135949283838272,0.026407239958643913,0.016369331628084183,-7.920151110738516E-4,0.008329012431204319,0.08046802878379822,0.043180543929338455,0.043235376477241516,0.04066846892237663,0.034671660512685776,0.020050624385476112,0.006609561387449503,-0.03303323686122894,0.021788401529192924,0.03752557188272476,-0.005985225085169077,0.02679155394434929,0.006966594140976667,0.009720219299197197,-0.023267926648259163,0.018038257956504822,0.027230188250541687,0.008815380744636059,0.017678700387477875,-0.06702575832605362,0.012886769138276577,-0.011982584372162819,0.0017572375945746899,-0.066929