(355, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1757415162795.mp3', 'compressed_1757415162795.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1757415162795.mp4', 'Hi, I\'m Kailash. I like to think of myself as someone who enjoys turning numbers into stories that drive decisions. My passion for finance started when I realized how my strategy lies behind every deal, every valuation and every market move. It\'s not just numbers, it\'s narratives. The shape of business. Currently I\'m pursuing my PGDM in Finance at MCC Boy Tunnel School of Business and recently did my internship with Prabhudasi Radar in Equity research that I didn\'t just analyze balance sheet. I dived deep into go fashion, stock building valuation models and benchmarking peers which taught me how critical position and clarity when advising investors. What excites me is working at the intersection of analytics and strategy where financial insights can be translated into decisions that unlock real business value. I bring a detail oriented approach, strong financial modeling skills and the ability to simplify complexity. More importantly, I bring curiosity and hunger to learn which I believe are key in such a fast paced environment.', 255, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1757415162795.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1757415162795.jpg', '2025-09-09 16:23:11.422766', 'C191', 'null', 'null', '[0.00721050426363945,-0.026083018630743027,-0.011237339116632938,0.0339759923517704,0.10234896093606949,0.06182144954800606,0.002441797172650695,0.029008571058511734,0.0264323428273201,-6.091345567256212E-4,-0.026001855731010437,0.01647009328007698,-0.02034883387386799,0.012614719569683075,0.007765990681946278,0.05677436292171478,0.06774628907442093,0.008787360042333603,0.025058068335056305,-0.009916313923895359,0.01622609794139862,0.064333476126194,0.03541174158453941,0.047532930970191956,0.03158900886774063,0.019445668905973434,0.03364086896181106