(356, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1757415543172.mp3', 'compressed_1757415543172.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1757415543172.mp4', 'Hello, I am Zarav Samson, pursuing my PGDM at MCC Boy Thomas School of Business in Human Resource Management. After completing my BCOM and Corporate Secretaryship, I have gained practical exposure through internships at VOC Port Authority where I worked on HR and supply chain processes like vessel scheduling, cargo documentation, and compliance workflows, and at Unibic Foods where I supported marketing and consumer analysis. I also engaged in a social immersion project with the Ahan foundation, contributing to the education and community initiatives. Beyond academics, I\'ve actively organized events, participated in clubs, and earned recognization such as the Best Manager award in an intercollegiate competition and prizes in photography contests. I am passionate about integrating HR and operations knowledge to enhance workforce productivity and contribute meaningfully to the organizational growth. Thank you.', 249, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1757415543172.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1757415543172.jpg', '2025-09-09 16:30:56.459138', 'C191', 'null', 'null', '[0.013175053521990776,0.00807798933237791,-0.03116922453045845,0.05035468190908432,0.09137839823961258,0.046951908618211746,-5.926459562033415E-4,0.027653926983475685,-7.74499902036041E-4,-0.005520896520465612,-0.03984040394425392,0.014795285649597645,-0.03164927661418915,0.013078704476356506,-0.0013623815029859543,0.05226803943514824,0.06834932416677475,0.01911068893969059,0.01869010180234909,-0.009278837591409683,0.018769552931189537,0.07010538876056671,0.06295526772737503,0.03288047015666962,0.05005967617034912,0.030126633122563362,0.03553210198879242,0.008599708788096905,-0.02180592715740204,0.023911025375127792,0.031846143305301666,-0.04026993364095688,0.028020445257425