(363, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1757424512197.mp3', 'compressed_1757424512197.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1757424512197.mp4', 'Hi, I\'m Santosh, currently pursuing my PGDM in Finance and Business analytics at MCC Boytown School of Business. I am passionate about solving business problem with both finance and data. Recently I was the part of winning team at Logitech Innovation where we developed a rural healthcare startup idea and received online grant. Currently I have done my internship at Ztafrani Automotive where I worked on estimating packing material cost, calculating unit per box, and analyzing raw material usage. I also handled GST reconciliation under the reverse charge mechanism by matching the vendor invoice with SAP and ensuring accurate input tax credit filings. All along I have built my skills in power, BI, Tableau, K9 and Excel which helped me to turn financial operations into insights. I have also taken up leadership roles like serving as some department forum representative during my UGS which taught me teamwork and communication. Thank you.', 227, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1757424512197.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1757424512197.jpg', '2025-09-09 18:59:30.333407', 'C191', 'null', 'null', '[0.014295995235443115,-0.008809104561805725,-0.01611814834177494,0.05584565922617912,0.10631921887397766,0.07390284538269043,-0.007147299125790596,0.02432822994887829,0.01932178996503353,-0.014282324351370335,-0.027368424460291862,0.013382882811129093,-0.028599241748452187,0.010888385586440563,0.0038806379307061434,0.0612744577229023,0.07194981724023819,0.026863688603043556,0.024711288511753082,-0.008741072379052639,0.01922714337706566,0.059728410094976425,0.04671473056077957,0.04429230839014053,0.040189020335674286,0.03520458564162254,0.026749830693006516,0.008477374911308289,-0.028691032901406288,0.007526265922933817,0.03491149842739105,-0.00920493