(369, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1757425941946.mp3', 'compressed_1757425941946.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1757425941946.mp4', 'Hello, I am Naveen Chandha. I am currently pursuing my PGDM in Supply Chain and Marketing at MCC Boyd Thailand School of Business. I hold a Bachelor\'s degree in BECOME Bank Management. I have interned at Madras Engineering Industries on the project Nilkaran model for the intra units in MEI and in which I contributed by collecting data workings on the value stream mapping and estimating the diesel cost and optimizing the routes and making it more cost efficient and also I have interned at Malayalamonorma as a Marketing and promotions intern by selling the magazines to various customers which helped me to learn about the customer segmentation and omnichannel marketing and customer behavior. With the blend of supply chain knowledge and marketing exposure and practical experience, I believe I can add value to your organization and contribute effective to achieve its goals. Thank you.', 251, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1757425941946.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1757425941946.jpg', '2025-09-09 19:22:50.620065', 'C191', 'null', 'null', '[0.01737946830689907,-0.006781367119401693,-0.008513957262039185,0.056861698627471924,0.10327580571174622,0.06720789521932602,0.0018899012356996536,0.048595692962408066,0.015019533224403858,0.0057980976998806,-0.022902583703398705,0.01803610660135746,-0.03381885960698128,0.016651468351483345,7.296947296708822E-4,0.06276765465736389,0.07509995251893997,0.01192291546612978,0.023311374709010124,-0.002050419570878148,0.02252854034304619,0.05838673934340477,0.057644154876470566,0.03643396496772766,0.035333115607500076,0.02423546090722084,0.02995937690138817,0.02190743014216423,-0.035304345190525055,0.006624461151659489,0.027639904990792274,-0.019762659445405006,0.029422229155898094,0.009203764609992504,0.02