(371, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1757426550396.mp3', 'compressed_1757426550396.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1757426550396.mp4', 'Hello, my name is Mohammad Asam. I am pursuing my PGDM in France at MCC Boydon School of Business. Over the years I have developed a strong interest in finance and data analytics and I enjoy translating numbers into meaningful business insights. I recently interned at Ashokrahan in Chennai where I worked in export finance and gained hands on experience in managing documentation and compilers for international trade. Alongside this, I created an interactive Power BI dashboard for the HR team which helped track and analyze employee performance more effectively. These experiences taught me how finance and data visualization can work together to improve decision making. In addition to academics, I have taken on leadership roles such as serving as the Vice President of Student Council and Treasurer of the Fitness Club. I also enjoy participating in debates, events and competitions where I have been recognized for communication and teamwork skills. Outside of work, I am passionate about sports, especially cricket, which has instilled in me qualities like discipline and focus. Going forward, I am eager to build a career in finance and analytics where I can contribute with both precision and creativity with continuing to learn and grow as professional. Thank you.', 267, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1757426550396.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1757426550396.jpg', '2025-09-09 19:35:49.840369', 'C191', 'null', 'null', '[-4.1439023334532976E-4,-0.010292861610651016,-0.018539350479841232,0.04491983354091644,0.08979510515928268,0.044639069586992264,-0.003118736669421196,0.027760092169046402,0.015073957853019238,-0.006337903905659914,-0.023952091112732887,0.005678827408701181,-0.03704138100147247,0.02213986963033676,0.017526088282465935,0.0619785