(385, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1757677582211.mp3', 'compressed_1757677582211.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1757677582211.mp4', 'Hello, my name is Samasa Sarte and I\'m pursuing my PhD at MGC Boyton School of Business. I did my summer internship at Progress Rural Capital where I created several Python applications through the leveraging of AI to measure the risk versus written over a long period of time over several indices. I\'ve also measured these indices through several simulations of the global financial Crisis and the COVID 19 crisis to show how investment strategies would pan out during these time periods. Now now for my undergraduate life, I was elected as a Creative Secretary through extensive campaigning for my department club Monetrix. In my personal life I\'m a hobby chess player and a hobby quizzer for both of which I\'ve collected several accolades in low level competitions. I also developed a trading algorithm, while not successful, has given me great insights. With my varied experiences I believe that I would be a great asset for any opportunity that would come across my way. Thank you.', 271, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1757677582211.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1757677582211.jpg', '2025-09-12 17:16:54.308358', 'C191', 'null', 'null', '[0.016527356579899788,-0.013437189161777496,-0.017053147777915,0.04819973558187485,0.09692708402872086,0.054992031306028366,0.003354861168190837,0.03815499693155289,0.01751888543367386,3.1399907311424613E-4,-0.010995752178132534,0.017491860315203667,-0.03064757026731968,0.018596773967146873,-0.006326771806925535,0.055682193487882614,0.0625748485326767,0.005643111187964678,0.013497119769454002,-0.015307122841477394,8.004631963558495E-4,0.07950785011053085,0.05098941549658775,0.040489282459020615,0.04583195969462395,0.0215158648788929,0.028068071231245995,-0.004022569395601749,-0.015855729579925537,0.00477275