(398, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1759902469707.mp3', 'compressed_1759902469707.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1759902469707.mp4', 'Hello, I\'m Margaret Bina, pursuing postgraduate Diploma in Management specializing in finance. My core strength lies in financial statement analytics, financial data analytics, portfolio management and financial modeling with the analytical tools like Power BI and Tableau for data driven decision making. I come with diversified internship background. As a supply chain intern at Lincoln Electric India, I worked under a project titled 3PL Warehouse evaluating the operational benefits of a warehouse relocation. As a Digital Marketing Marketing intern at Mind Skills, I contributed to the business engagement initiatives and supported the market research. Beyond academics, I volunteered myself as the tutor for the children from the Narika river community, an experience which was both humbling and rewarding. I look forward to apply and upgrade my skills and contribute to the dynamic professional environment. Thank you.', 216, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1759902469707.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1759902469707.jpg', '2025-10-08 11:18:58.730361', 'C191', 'null', 'null', '[0.03205345571041107,-0.016094250604510307,-0.0049691153690218925,0.049898553639650345,0.09709235280752182,0.06887480616569519,-0.005915398709475994,0.03469201922416687,0.01755427196621895,0.006879946682602167,-0.026454592123627663,0.022420521825551987,-0.027560213580727577,0.028705812990665436,0.001261048368178308,0.047894187271595,0.0749836415052414,0.01989443600177765,0.007903845980763435,-0.020925266668200493,0.012089710682630539,0.06065015494823456,0.050747424364089966,0.028530439361929893,0.0226266011595726,0.026508919894695282,0.03645608574151993,9.305693092755973E-4,-0.025423424318432808,0.012348110787570477,0.03420256823301315,-0.010378394275903702,0.0238818395