(401, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1759919228055.mp3', 'compressed_1759919228055.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1759919228055.mp4', 'Hello, I am Shahul Amit, driven by leadership mindset and keen interest in decision making. Currently pursuing my post graduation Diploma in Management in Finance with a minor in Business analytics at MCC Boytana School of Business. I also hold a Bachelor\'s Degree in Commerce from Madraska State College. At MRF limited I worked as Financial Analyst intern. I advised the company on a capital expansion project through a feasibility analysis model. I also conducted a vendor assessment for a water retreatment project recommending the most cost efficient and financially soundful option. I have developed an entrepreneurial outlook and problem solving approach by creating my own startup named ruralmit which focuses on delivering medicinal services to rural doorsteps. At MCC MRF Innovation Park I worked on Lean Database Management while my community engagement with Volunteer for India strengthened my leadership and teamwork. Skilled in Excel, Power Bay and other data analytics tools, I am eager to apply my analytical and financial expertise to create measurable impact. Thank you.', 241, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1759919228055.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1759919228055.jpg', '2025-10-08 15:58:01.763412', 'C191', 'null', 'null', '[0.0168035626411438,-0.020185617730021477,-0.00909043475985527,0.04706960916519165,0.1032688245177269,0.06226813793182373,-6.565911462530494E-5,0.02460344508290291,0.011730975471436977,0.004763806704431772,-0.03486647456884384,0.01791205443441868,-0.03918749839067459,0.022934071719646454,-1.706445764284581E-4,0.061788756400346756,0.0715155154466629,0.0061905779875814915,0.016452515497803688,-0.00462269177660346,0.015264173969626427,0.07571126520633698,0.062012679874897,0.04252607375383377,0.04253363236784935,0