(405, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1760033975610.mp3', 'compressed_1760033975610.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1760033975610.mp4', 'Hello, I\'m Soni Divya Sri Jawahar, a passionate PGDM student specializing in supply Chain Management at MCC Boydana School of Business. With a strong commerce background, I have hands on experience from internships at Lincoln Electric and Biocon limited where I worked on inventory management, demand and supply gap alignment and inbound logistics. I am skilled in Excel automation, Tableau Power, BI and few data analytical tools which I have applied to improve the efficiency and decision making in the real world supply chain operations. I have also earned few certifications in Retail management, supply chain Optimization and data analytics. I\'m passionate about streamlining the processes and driving the operational excellence and I\'m looking forward to applying my skills in the real world dynamic business environment. Thank you.', 231, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1760033975610.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1760033975610.jpg', '2025-10-09 23:51:02.360572', 'C191', 'null', 'null', '[0.01727554202079773,-0.0021435576491057873,-0.013270240277051926,0.04621461406350136,0.1078641340136528,0.06973809003829956,-0.00554453581571579,0.03906399384140968,9.735901257954538E-4,0.008922056294977665,-0.019462795928120613,0.004915066994726658,-0.04620624706149101,0.026303226128220558,0.0019226537551730871,0.06603485345840454,0.06756190210580826,0.023967528715729713,0.018180575221776962,-0.004967442713677883,0.024748727679252625,0.059147801250219345,0.0377633161842823,0.044408977031707764,0.04094843938946724,0.014988753944635391,0.028806746006011963,0.030522918328642845,-0.036404799669981,3.896102716680616E-4,0.036529045552015305,-0.031764693558216095,0.038818683475255966,0.012990321964025497,0.03124251216650009,0.005544811021536589,0.01417571026