(406, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1760067809727.mp3', 'compressed_1760067809727.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1760067809727.mp4', 'Hi, I\'m Jane Jarlan, a PGDM student at MCC Boy Tanyan School of Business, specializing in finance. I see every opportunity as a chance to learn, grow, and create an impact. During my internship at Ashok Leyland, I explored the light commercial vehicle sector, analyze the market trends, and it gave me confidence on connecting data with real business outcomes. I also worked with ACE Innovation as a content writer for the organization\'s digital newsletter, which enhanced my storytelling skills and communication skills. As a part of my social immersion project at MCC Family Life Institute, I worked with rural women entrepreneurs to enhance the reach of their handmade products. It helped me develop empathy and understand how thoughtful business support can truly impact lives. Along with pgdm, I\'m also pursuing HSCA to strengthen my expertise in finance and contribute meaningfully to the organization\'s success. Thank you.', 217, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1760067809727.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1760067809727.jpg', '2025-10-10 09:14:25.685584', 'C191', 'null', 'null', '[0.007115330547094345,-0.01032425556331873,-0.015569369308650494,0.03862980008125305,0.09768573194742203,0.05414808541536331,0.019326291978359222,0.030237261205911636,0.0033020914997905493,-0.0047225626185536385,-0.025709638372063637,0.00629639346152544,-0.02355620451271534,0.01942872814834118,-0.0066200434230268,0.04467723146080971,0.06834809482097626,0.01943873055279255,0.011015093885362148,-0.0047344183549284935,0.009007039479911327,0.05968733876943588,0.031555697321891785,0.044557131826877594,0.025132514536380768,0.016835052520036697,0.035252101719379425,0.004377961158752441,-0.0351567342877388,0.002806556411087513,0.03050108253955841,-0.031200865283608437,0.