(409, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1760096511364.mp3', 'compressed_1760096511364.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1760096511364.mp4', 'Hi, I\'m Narkish. I\'m currently pursuing my PGDM with a major in Marketing and minor in Supply Chain and Operations. I hold a Bachelor\'s degree in BCOM Corporate Secretaryship from Atraj College for Women. I interned at Global Logistics India Solution Private Limited in NNOCC department where I worked on market research, lead generation, client engagement and export import documentation, gaining exposure to link between marketing and logistics. I also worked as a social media intern at Natural Spade 3 Salon, managing content creation and campaigns that boosted Salon\'s Instagram visibility and engagement. I have done a social media campaign with Kuda NGO earlier. I organized hostel events during my undergraduate studies, developing leadership, event management and communication skills. With this background, I\'m eager to contribute to a dynamic organization and continue growing in my career. Thank you.', 221, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1760096511364.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1760096511364.jpg', '2025-10-10 17:12:52.828855', 'C191', 'null', 'null', '[0.019275397062301636,-0.012388307601213455,-0.005204357206821442,0.04166977480053902,0.0978432297706604,0.06769967824220657,0.004288361873477697,0.03442114219069481,0.014286463148891926,0.0073076216503977776,-0.032020628452301025,0.005947161931544542,-0.03073335438966751,0.010558899492025375,0.01912425085902214,0.0661458894610405,0.07480231672525406,0.03027258813381195,0.014765524305403233,-0.012009459547698498,0.03557738661766052,0.05740310624241829,0.046584103256464005,0.03597165271639824,0.04486864432692528,0.02185651659965515,0.027602169662714005,0.011573929339647293,-0.037335000932216644,0.014423353597521782,0.03572827950119972,-0.031526558101177216,0.02621845155954361,0.0