(410, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1760113873145.mp3', 'compressed_1760113873145.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1760113873145.mp4', 'Holding an undergraduation in Commerce Professional Accounting from Madras Kristian College. I\'m currently doing my PhD in Finance and Marketing in MCC Boyd Tandon School of Business. I\'ve always had a passion for finance and marketing together. I\'ve also completed my internship at Aldi Button Capserv Pvt Ltd firm and investment banking firm. Since it was a startup firm, I was able to learn a lot of concepts about investment banking and how an investment banking firm operates. Apart from academics, I\'ve also completed my social immersion project at nawa, a not for profit organization in OT where we work towards contributing towards the needs of the tribal communities of Nilgiris. There are about six tribal communities in the whole of Tamil Nadu and we presented the queries before the government. As far as my creative skills are concerned, I\'m also a pianist and I\'m ready and eager to contribute and integrate my professional and creative skills towards building the organization and towards building myself. Thank you.', 219, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1760113873145.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1760113873145.jpg', '2025-10-10 22:02:40.897489', '', 'null', 'null', '[0.019763801246881485,-0.0048207794316112995,-0.011525970883667469,0.03883517533540726,0.10150598734617233,0.06019848957657814,0.009340767748653889,0.030722539871931076,0.01801230199635029,0.008123660460114479,-0.03220854327082634,0.010211034677922726,-0.02914985455572605,0.02485523745417595,0.010811437852680683,0.0568905808031559,0.06872665882110596,0.02090482786297798,0.01364847831428051,-0.014630001038312912,0.01083178911358118,0.07690984755754471,0.055573347955942154,0.04576587304472923,0.05253484845161438,0.03450517728924751,0.03656904399394989,0.0098213544115