(411, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1760155827574.mp3', 'compressed_1760155827574.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1760155827574.mp4', 'Hi, I\'m Niveta S. An aspiring financial analyst with a solid background in finance and Business analytics. I\'m currently pursuing my postgraduate Diploma in Management at MCC Boytown School of Business specializing in finance and Business analytics. I hold a Bachelor\'s Degree in Professional Accounting and have also cleared CMA Foundation. During my internship at Lincoln Entry Company, I gained hands on experience in sales incentive computation, freight subsidy analysis and SAP based financial operations. Additionally, through my social immersion with Hand in Hand India, I conducted a data driven study on the socio economic impact of Sustainable Village Project. I\'m proficient in msxl, TALLY and Power bi and I\'m also passionate about using data insights to support sound financial decision making. I aspire to build my career where I can apply analytical thinking and financial expertise to drive organizational growth and efficiency. Thank you.', 238, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1760155827574.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1760155827574.jpg', '2025-10-11 09:43:04.469157', 'C191', 'null', 'null', '[0.01777772605419159,-0.016027674078941345,-0.004612306132912636,0.036885324865579605,0.10329204052686691,0.06787674129009247,-0.009485116228461266,0.03294547647237778,0.011760130524635315,0.013340783305466175,-0.023639971390366554,0.015299631282687187,-0.034164249897003174,0.01127209234982729,0.008406597189605236,0.05791988596320152,0.07700536400079727,0.02351664938032627,0.021017294377088547,-0.021319834515452385,0.016071641817688942,0.07285168766975403,0.05189940333366394,0.04033506661653519,0.04196297377347946,0.028924252837896347,0.02932167612016201,-4.7408684622496367E-4,-0.021134663373231888,0.004491882864385843,0.035938303917646