(414, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1760351880469.mp3', 'compressed_1760351880469.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1760351880469.mp4', 'Good morning everyone. I am Srivajani Velu, currently pursuing my PGDM in Finance at MCC Boyd Tannen School of Business. I bring enhanced experience from internships Ashok Leyland, Madras Engineering Industries and Randy Formulations where I worked on projects like Supplier Satisfaction Survey, Cost and ratio analysis and financial reporting. These gave me a strong exposure to data analysis, supply chain process and corporate finance. I am skilled in tools like Excel, Tableau, Power, BI and Tally and I have presented insights directly to the senior management strateg, strengthening both my analytical and communication skills. Beyond academics, I actively contribute to community development initiatives and enjoy creative pursuits like drawing and music. I see myself as adaptable, detail oriented and driven to deliver results and I\'m eager to contribute my skills in finance and data driven decision making to create measurable impact. Thank you.', 275, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1760351880469.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1760351880469.jpg', '2025-10-13 16:08:39.851244', 'C191', 'null', 'null', '[0.025334471836686134,0.0017366972751915455,-0.014117240905761719,0.053815726190805435,0.11030412465333939,0.07029431313276291,-0.009252479299902916,0.02661263383924961,-0.0066123660653829575,-0.015179997310042381,-0.024209821596741676,0.01604132354259491,-0.03071771189570427,0.018082886934280396,0.013160436414182186,0.057060983031988144,0.07431046664714813,0.01985614001750946,0.023316387087106705,-0.0041629658080637455,0.025103220716118813,0.06817856431007385,0.042390625923871994,0.0370386503636837,0.03266351670026779,0.023561779409646988,0.03496261686086655,0.00206148624420166,-0.02679460123181343,0.012698521837592125,0.04453893005847931