(417, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1761552416843.mp3', 'compressed_1761552416843.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1761552416843.mp4', 'Hi, I\'m Rosemary. I\'m currently pursuing my PGDM from MCC Boy Talent School of Business. I describe myself to be a positive and a disciplined person who enjoys learning and taking on new challenges. During my internship at Madras Engineering Industries, I got hands on experience in digital marketing working on search engine, optimizing the website, designing the product catalog, and designing a visual aid for their loyalty program Mei Mitra. It has helped me understand how digital strategies can transform a brand\'s presence and connect better with their customers. I\'m looking forward to build my career in corporate sector, especially in marketing and brand strategy where I can use both my creative and analytical side to make an impact. Thank you.', 210, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1761552416843.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1761552416843.jpg', '2025-10-27 13:45:02.988305', '', 'null', 'null', '[0.013822067528963089,-0.00576221477240324,0.0035025973338633776,0.04792569577693939,0.10510452091693878,0.0576198436319828,-0.002148790517821908,0.03799976408481598,0.017247242853045464,0.0036514238454401493,-0.031188348308205605,0.011439356952905655,-0.021769076585769653,0.005143265705555677,-0.013310439884662628,0.055253766477108,0.060717325657606125,0.030831392854452133,0.015757346525788307,-0.005616469774395227,0.014945825561881065,0.07189501821994781,0.049571286886930466,0.04437461867928505,0.04166843742132187,0.02814948372542858,0.04066029563546181,0.013551061041653156,-0.03591907396912575,0.013358541764318943,0.03871745243668556,-0.030372880399227142,0.02679482288658619,0.012212790548801422,0.023635830730199814,-0.01319904811680317,0.027516480535268784,0.03643157333135605,0.014722762629389763,7.179791573435068E-4,-0.086173944175