(420, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1761570873587.mp3', 'compressed_1761570873587.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1761570873587.mp4', 'Hi, I\'m Rupa Kalyani. I completed my BCom at Tiagarajar College. There I have an opportunity to organize a management event which helped me to develop strong leadership and time management skills. I was also honored by Best Outgoing Student of the Year. Currently I am pursuing PGDM at MCC Boydhan School of Business. During my short term industry engagement at Axis Bank, I gained hands on exposure in loan, investment and music. That\'s where my interest in finance began. During my summer internship at Sundaram Rubber Factory, I worked on improving the lead time and reducing cost which helped me to understand the connection between finance and logistics. Overall, these experience made me proactive curious to apply in real world business environment.', 208, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1761570873587.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1761570873587.jpg', '2025-10-27 18:45:21.671039', 'C191', 'null', 'null', '[0.028391990810632706,-0.022755112498998642,-0.002459304640069604,0.03086905926465988,0.10080517828464508,0.05933499336242676,-0.005231338087469339,0.03596777841448784,0.006610196549445391,0.015604848973453045,-0.026612356305122375,0.014486112631857395,-0.02664470486342907,0.01961253024637699,0.01031969953328371,0.06061742082238197,0.07153035700321198,0.024511709809303284,0.025602808222174644,-4.4148365850560367E-4,0.027558982372283936,0.07282567769289017,0.061845071613788605,0.05178949609398842,0.04160728305578232,0.019723547622561455,0.02900569885969162,0.007504105567932129,-0.020869290456175804,0.01421292033046484,0.04405036196112633,-0.018327048048377037,0.02096465602517128,0.023929018527269363,0.027245474979281425,-0.013148766942322254,0.021635401993989944,0.040622174739837646,0.009996786713600159,0.0025673822965472937,-0.0796492