(421, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1761630800395.mp3', 'compressed_1761630800395.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1761630800395.mp4', 'Hi, I\'m NCR and I see myself as a creative strategist who can turn ideas into digital stories that connect with people. Currently pursuing my Postgraduate Diploma in Management at NCC Boy Tynen School of Business, I have done my internship at Mindskills where I have helped to launch a learning management system by designing the content that made learning more engaging. I have also driven influencer collaboration at Groom India Salon and Spa to amplify the brand visibility and I have also volunteered with Youth for Seva at Hyderabad where I have contributed my cultural skills to the children from government schools. Beyond work, I channel my creativity through dance, drawing and videography, which often inspires my professional project. My goal is to build a personal brand around it with someone who brings strategy, storytelling and innovation together to help brand engage with the audience in meaningful ways. Thank you.', 237, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1761630800395.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1761630800395.jpg', '2025-10-28 11:24:17.558057', 'C191', 'null', 'null', '[0.03801846504211426,0.004861097317188978,-0.0026566896121948957,0.04691779986023903,0.0971672385931015,0.055755507200956345,0.010892725549638271,0.027280721813440323,0.014333177357912064,0.012200143188238144,-0.04331086948513985,0.012606402859091759,-0.021692190319299698,0.022748105227947235,0.0015704649267718196,0.06267674267292023,0.05995085462927818,0.022356150671839714,0.01506446860730648,5.947051104158163E-4,0.008183998055756092,0.05500839278101921,0.04520079493522644,0.045935649424791336,0.042388226836919785,0.019437063485383987,0.037418875843286514,0.01026171538978815,-0.03830169513821602,0.023977115750312805,0.02737041749060154,-0.01749979518353939,0.02