(423, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1762149489547.mp3', 'compressed_1762149489547.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1762149489547.mp4', 'Hi, I am Verla. Pursuing my PGDM in Marketing and Business analytics at MCC Boydton School of Business, I gained practical experiences through internships. At MRF Limited I conducted market research with 90 taxi operators on TYREVS patents and at Malayalam Manaroma, I drove sufficient sales through practical and marketing techniques. Through Assisted Social Immersion program, I carried out fitness assessments for entrepreneurship football players and organized tournaments to empower women in sports. Earlier, as an Omnisport leader at Decathlon, I achieved sales targets and improved customer engagement through events. I bring skills in marketing, research, sales and analytics with hands on tools like Python, Excel, Power Bi and Tableau. Beyond academics, I am passionate about football and leadership. As a founder of Ariella United Football Club and convener of B School Sports and Fitness Club, I look forward to contributing to organizations that value insights, innovation and teamwork. Thank you.', 266, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1762149489547.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1762149489547.jpg', '2025-11-03 11:29:09.478715', 'C191', 'null', 'null', '[0.020282579585909843,-0.003416279563680291,-0.016595330089330673,0.0459146685898304,0.10260193049907684,0.05592804029583931,0.008795778267085552,0.03108849935233593,0.013258740305900574,0.0024274548050016165,-0.028607040643692017,0.011694432236254215,-0.03215362876653671,0.013822441920638084,-0.0024235777091234922,0.05689406767487526,0.06555191427469254,0.03352150321006775,0.01830901764333248,0.0014848005957901478,0.017087290063500404,0.07945287972688675,0.04342351853847504,0.04769981652498245,0.0399169847369194,0.01954118348658085,0.039500895887613297,0.00861477293074131,-0.03854796290