(424, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1762162233557.mp3', 'compressed_1762162233557.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1762162233557.mp4', 'Hi, this is Vaishali. I\'m currently pursuing my PhDM in supply chain Management at MCC Boyd Tendon School of Business. I recently completed my internship at Triway Forwarders Private Limited where I worked on export and import documentation, handled essential process, coordinated with clients and monitor the cargo delivery updates. This gave me a hands on experience in understanding international logistics and documentation flow. In addition, I worked on a research project with Global Logistics focusing on optimization of inland container deposit in India for improving the supply chain efficiency. Through this experience I have strengthened my knowledge in supply chain digitization operations and coordination and I look forward to applying these skills to contribute effectively in supply chain role. Thank you.', 247, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1762162233557.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1762162233557.jpg', '2025-11-03 15:01:11.499500', 'C191', '', 'null', '[0.028386469930410385,0.012430442497134209,-0.016634611412882805,0.04628363996744156,0.10819798707962036,0.06829095631837845,-0.004012431018054485,0.04196789488196373,-0.0011341157369315624,-0.0044053238816559315,-0.014633486978709698,0.006489246152341366,-0.035153161734342575,0.03207872435450554,-9.699875372461975E-4,0.06294665485620499,0.07285424321889877,0.01718989387154579,0.006131279282271862,-0.004589227493852377,0.012337950989603996,0.06586506217718124,0.041995853185653687,0.035967618227005005,0.04183462634682655,0.013026966713368893,0.022894326597452164,0.017102500423789024,-0.04071935638785362,0.0017868565628305078,0.03632696345448494,-0.031900614500045776,0.025413883849978447,0.007549588102847338,0.015763770788908005,-0.006440837401896715,0.004960852675139904,0.0272