(428, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1762165019882.mp3', 'compressed_1762165019882.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1762165019882.mp4', 'Hi, I am Michael Nruto. I am eager to start my career in the field of marketing. Currently I am pursuing my postgraduate Diploma in Management with a specialization in Marketing at MCG Boy Tando School of Business. I done internship at Sundar Fasteners Ltd. Where I conducted Tender based marketing research coordinated Tender submission. Also I did internship in Devine Foods where I analyzed market trends, planned promotional activities and engaged with customers to enhance brand visibility. I also contributed to an NGO which is Vivega Arcadelli where I prepared CSR proposals and managed their social media presence to strengthen their community engagement. I am skilled in Excel, Power, bi, Tableau and Python and have completed certification in A in Marketing, International Business, Microsoft, Excel and Statistics. I am passionate about combining marketing insight with technology to drive business growth. Thank you for watching.', 252, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1762165019882.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1762165019882.jpg', '2025-11-03 15:48:16.984189', 'C191', '', 'null', '[0.026545671746134758,0.004139930475503206,0.011711124330759048,0.041653938591480255,0.09586707502603531,0.06573940813541412,-0.0028593684546649456,0.035002902150154114,0.014333581551909447,0.0055677820928394794,-0.04550669342279434,0.028497088700532913,-0.025518372654914856,0.014350706711411476,0.012532509863376617,0.06358137726783752,0.07018907368183136,0.030677758157253265,0.023505646735429764,0.005930950865149498,0.009854737669229507,0.08046109974384308,0.03856977820396423,0.03816114366054535,0.05397643521428108,0.022045787423849106,0.029278617352247238,0.013098936527967453,-0.043348751962184906,0.007489996496587992,0.03534077852964401,-0.0094581674784421