(434, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1763305567501.mp3', 'compressed_1763305567501.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1763305567501.mp4', 'Hello, I am Alisha Nazgar from Kolkata. I have completed my graduation from J.D. billa Institute, Department of Management with a specialization in Finance. Apart from my academics, I have completed two internships. One during my graduation in bank of India where I was in the savings department and one during my MBA in the Outlook Group. In Outlook Group, my internship was divided into two phases. In the first phase, I was given a task of customer acquisition where I had to sell magazines worth 10,000 which within two weeks. And in the second phase, my internship was in the finance domain where I had to create investment portfolios for different income classes and analyze payment gateways for the Outlook Group. Apart from this, I believe I\'m a team player because I\'m a part of annual fest committee at IFMR where I lead a team of 10 members. Thank you.', 329, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1763305567501.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1763305567501.jpg', '2025-11-16 20:36:39.735278', 'J007', 'null', 'null', '[0.029879461973905563,-0.01599021442234516,0.004906917922198772,0.03678854927420616,0.10203955322504044,0.053408779203891754,-0.0050827390514314175,0.03835073858499527,0.019825875759124756,0.009091123007237911,-0.029598863795399666,0.01248857844620943,-0.03188035637140274,0.014498214237391949,0.023278268054127693,0.0436396487057209,0.07103089988231659,0.02164568193256855,0.005794064607471228,-0.0015972887631505728,0.02645958587527275,0.08202546089887619,0.06150628998875618,0.04102780297398567,0.05643642321228981,0.018282607197761536,0.028016503900289536,0.005082458723336458,-0.03525463491678238,0.025078140199184418,0.03512798622250557,-0.024421194568276405,0.004836040083318949,0.0192323699593544,0.033095501363277435,-0.0230167023