(435, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1763306081567.mp3', 'compressed_1763306081567.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1763306081567.mp4', 'My name is Amania. I\'m currently pursuing my MBA with a specialization in the marketing and finance. I also have the background in computer science as well. I\'m someone who genuinely enjoys interacting with the people, understanding their needs, helping them to make informed decisions which naturally aligns with the customer relationship management role. During my mba, I worked on projects related to the market research, bias behavior and also sales strategy which helped me to develop the strong communication and presentation and also problem solving skills. I\'m good at building the trust trust, listening to the customers and explaining the solutions, clarity and I am motivated, quick to learn and comfortable in handling the multiple tasks. Overall, I bring a mix of analytical thinking and strong people skills. I\'m excited to grow the sales and customer relationship management role.', 338, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1763306081567.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1763306081567.jpg', '2025-11-16 20:45:21.866200', 'J007', 'null', 'null', '[0.00888737477362156,0.006651605945080519,-9.86794475466013E-4,0.05216919630765915,0.10554273426532745,0.04052334651350975,0.022641494870185852,0.023906372487545013,0.00644109258428216,0.011297827586531639,-0.042731188237667084,0.023345040157437325,-0.02902042120695114,0.012934302911162376,-0.010509500280022621,0.05085151642560959,0.06336287409067154,0.024323444813489914,0.01879155822098255,-0.006823479663580656,-0.0026087374426424503,0.0686747282743454,0.05204681307077408,0.046097610145807266,0.044749900698661804,0.026794057339429855,0.041420456022024155,0.014186103828251362,-0.027964962646365166,0.018725614994764328,0.01967129483819008,-0.03713783621788025,0.028517186641693115,0.013608436100184