(438, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1763307796531.mp3', 'compressed_1763307796531.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1763307796531.mp4', 'Hi, I\'m Mohit Acharya, someone who enjoys solving problem using data. During my internship at Patterson Securities, I built a Python based backtesting model for an option strategy and a Z score based pairs trading model which sparked my interest towards market and risk. I worked on multiple projects like dcf, valuation of Mariko on Excel, Netflix, consumer based consumer study using spss, and the Profit Protein Beverage strategy that won the first runners up at the Business Plan Hackathon. I\'ve also led my team to a first runners of finish at the national level Guer competition 2025. I have taken leadership roles here at IFMR as a class representative and I\'ve captained my college football team for three consecutive years during my ug. I\'m excited to bring a mix of analytical thinking with the ownership.', 341, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1763307796531.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1763307796531.jpg', '2025-11-16 21:16:53.827076', 'J007', 'null', 'null', '[0.004804265219718218,-0.013478593900799751,-0.02156142331659794,0.0669030174612999,0.10812254250049591,0.056155815720558167,-0.007336015347391367,0.0304707083851099,0.027132457122206688,-9.259165381081402E-4,-0.023751217871904373,0.023446911945939064,-0.036250241100788116,0.014474652707576752,-0.005502424668520689,0.04821278899908066,0.07468431442975998,0.012059645727276802,0.021818727254867554,-0.007678039837628603,9.967958612833172E-5,0.06149347871541977,0.03948424011468887,0.02565006911754608,0.03290523216128349,0.008260237984359264,0.013975398615002632,0.0011446380522102118,-0.028462426736950874,0.020232176408171654,0.03506402298808098,-0.013100164011120796,0.010324518196284771,2.139704974979395E-6,0.01726406067609787,-5.770424613729119E-4,0.0024819907266646624,0.044668