(441, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1763308571425.mp3', 'compressed_1763308571425.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1763308571425.mp4', 'Hi, my name is Kunal Singh, I was born in Boyta Banajmeer, Rajasthan. I\'m a person who turns conversations into opportunities and do have a problem solving approach as well. I bring 23 months of experience as a customer support executive where my job role was to solve the queries of the customer related to an antivirus product. I was transferred to the sales department and there I was pitching the customers to upgrade and cross sell their Norton product and I also worked as a floor support where I was handling a team of 20 members with my team leaders and I was handling the KPIs and workflow of day to day operations and my MBA. I worked with Grant Thomton and with a live project. There I was worked with 50 plus Kirana stores knowing about their problems and giving them recommendations to how increase their sales in day to day market. Apart from that I worked in Global Forum for Sustainable Transformation where I learned about AI and machine learning and I got to know how to work with a particular data with the help of AI machine learning. So I\'m looking forward for opportunities where I can apply this mindset. Thank you.', 323, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1763308571425.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1763308571425.jpg', '2025-11-16 21:26:40.745995', 'J007', '', 'null', '[0.027873653918504715,-0.01048616599291563,-2.262880589114502E-4,0.042974263429641724,0.0937296599149704,0.05954805761575699,0.01028276514261961,0.03936528414487839,0.03504866734147072,0.0053805080242455006,-0.053117234259843826,0.017247945070266724,-0.034341488033533096,0.012149541638791561,0.0036609952803701162,0.05182887986302376,0.053701162338256836,0.016841499134898186,0.013911144807934761,0.007499732077121735,0.011099284514784813,0.05473209172487259,0.049222