(447, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1763310967366.mp3', 'compressed_1763310967366.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1763310967366.mp4', 'Hi, I\'m Neelam Mehgasham. I am from Tirupati. I did my Btech in Electrical and Electronics Engineering from Saastra University, Trichy. Currently I am doing my MBA at IFMR with a specialization in Marketing. Here I also serve as the President of Student Council. Prior to this I was working as Assistant Project Manager as well as site engineer at VCR & Co. Where I used to implement and execute small scale as well as large scale electrical infrastructure products by coordinating with a lot of stakeholders. I also have an internship with IBM in the digital sales field where my role was to sell and design a go to market strategy for the flagship WatsonNext AI where I was successful in cross selling and upselling various IBM products. I also have an internship with Heredisa Electricals which is a leading transformer manufacturing plant. I also have certificates in the field of Retail Management and Project Management. I also have academic projects for Starbucks where we use various market research techniques and analyze the Starbucks. I also led a digital market campaign for Stories of Bangalore page by using various SEO techniques and a B testing.', 350, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1763310967366.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1763310967366.jpg', '2025-11-16 22:07:12.713538', 'J007', 'null', 'null', '[0.0282079316675663,-0.012762822210788727,-0.004012190271168947,0.04551776126027107,0.10142198950052261,0.050783075392246246,-9.846506145549938E-5,0.04653897508978844,0.015742339193820953,0.015136427246034145,-0.041711676865816116,0.01414122898131609,-0.03365830332040787,0.02900855243206024,-0.013903321698307991,0.05502273514866829,0.0728672444820404,0.01173485815525055,0.00955856405198574,0.0074136932380497456,0.017788879573345184,0.0689