(448, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1763311122614.mp3', 'compressed_1763311122614.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1763311122614.mp4', 'Hi, I\'m Srinathi. I enjoy understanding people, asking the right questions, and connecting needs with solutions. That\'s the space where I work the best. During my internship at Kabota Marketing agency, I handled B2B outreach for manufacturing and logistics clients, qualified leads, and handled conversations with CxOs and founders to understand their requirements. This taught me how to listen for real problems. As a part of my academic project, I\'ve done a multi platform digital marketing campaign which has crossed over 7 million views organically and outside class. I manage committees and I\'ve also coordinated with several sponsorship conversions and I\'m also currently writing a research paper on understanding the consumer behavior behind why people go for music premium services, which helped me sharpen my thinking about why people choose what they choose. Thank you.', 319, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1763311122614.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1763311122614.jpg', '2025-11-16 22:09:23.851475', 'J007', '', 'null', '[0.028011014685034752,0.004903807770460844,0.004500549752265215,0.04660160467028618,0.09293986856937408,0.06107373163104057,0.004981841426342726,0.038287922739982605,0.01966099627315998,0.007976332679390907,-0.027001382783055305,0.01820313185453415,-0.03292062506079674,0.008871152065694332,-0.010004019364714622,0.05617227777838707,0.060410089790821075,0.02457568235695362,0.020058341324329376,0.010020445100963116,0.014353415928781033,0.07672905921936035,0.03999725729227066,0.04028922691941261,0.04951042681932449,0.01684950292110443,0.025670059025287628,0.007873243652284145,-0.04405982419848442,0.012211065739393234,0.038179297000169754,-0.020422738045454025,0.019185392186045647,-5.557425902225077E-4,0.018369307741522