(461, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1763313462425.mp3', 'compressed_1763313462425.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1763313462425.mp4', 'Hi, I\'m Ganesh. I\'m doing my MBA at ifmr. I like working with the buyers and figuring out what they actually need so I can help them make clearer decisions. At Kranjiro Transport, I used to deal with the buyers and partners every day. That helped me understand their issues quickly and explain the things in a simple way so the work keeps moving without the confusion. Then at Empadisadha Sutra, I made climb decks and explain insights to the investors, which really improved how I present the things and how I build the trust through clear communication. My projects also helped me understand what drives a buyer\'s decision and how to turn that into something they can act on. And leading 120 credits in NCC taught me discipline and staying steady when there is a pressure. So I am looking for a role where communication targets and unbiased friendship matters. So that\'s why I feel the BRM rolled. 8 lndisofin fits me well.', 364, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1763313462425.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1763313462425.jpg', '2025-11-16 22:48:03.238190', 'J007', '', 'null', '[0.013349496759474277,-0.011654870584607124,-2.1657608158420771E-4,0.04744464159011841,0.09294944256544113,0.05384976789355278,0.01311931200325489,0.02551325410604477,0.03257063403725624,0.008390780538320541,-0.02188189886510372,0.05654556676745415,-0.030123986303806305,0.025563132017850876,0.008432180620729923,0.05737444758415222,0.07019022852182388,0.007717982400208712,0.01628253608942032,-0.011252949945628643,0.018575862050056458,0.07020781189203262,0.047293879091739655,0.04070860892534256,0.044966064393520355,0.02433961071074009,0.03634589910507202,0.00898790918290615,-0.0336267463862896,0.00881898496299982,0.030905134975910187,-0.022955557331442833,0.007351460400968