(466, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1763314541166.mp3', 'compressed_1763314541166.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1763314541166.mp4', 'Hi, my name is Mukul and I am from the Raja Notrakhand. I am someone who is quite passionate and hard working towards my work and this is quite evident during my journey. Also, I worked at Finletics during my summer internship as a market research intern and was involved in multiple projects, but I was somehow getting stuck between my tasks. So I end up in taking some time to think on it and broke the task into multiple steps and then shared it with my team. This has really helped me in taking responsibilities and managing my team. Another instance was during our annual event for Speakers Club where we had little time to conduct that event, but I delegated my task and decided who should do what. This has really helped me boosting my confidence and planning out events quite efficiently. I\'m also very sports lover and was in National Credit Corps too where I learned patience, discipline and how to stay calm under pressure.', 340, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1763314541166.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1763314541166.jpg', '2025-11-16 23:07:51.008088', 'J007', 'null', 'null', '[0.026481961831450462,-0.029495658352971077,-0.005096282809972763,0.037461988627910614,0.08234254270792007,0.055680714547634125,0.005430446472018957,0.019129445776343346,0.017122909426689148,-0.0018883808515965939,-0.014054729603230953,0.028678106144070625,-0.03546438738703728,0.025347258895635605,-0.003646161174401641,0.055164121091365814,0.05786431208252907,0.01695629581809044,7.588464650325477E-4,-0.006719666533172131,0.021502815186977386,0.08084087818861008,0.05306074395775795,0.051248759031295776,0.046903885900974274,0.021376337856054306,0.01565929688513279,-0.004425437189638615,-0.03116575814783573,0.021979402750730515,0.025402778759598732,-0.016072124242