(471, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1763315799789.mp3', 'compressed_1763315799789.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1763315799789.mp4', 'Hi, I\'m Yuktashree. I\'m an MBA student at Kriya University specializing in finance. Recently I have completed my summer internship at Global Forum for Sustainable Transformations as a Data Science Engineering intern where I worked on real time livestock farmers data to find potential farmers who need help from the government. This internship helped me to improve my data communication skills like communicating deep insights to stakeholders through visualizations and simple charts. Apart from this, during my MBA I have gained good knowledge on business valuations, portfolio optimizations and derivatives and recently I have discovered my strengths in leadership qualities. That\'s a brief about me and thank you.', 348, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1763315799789.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1763315799789.jpg', '2025-11-16 23:27:18.171452', 'J007', 'null', 'null', '[0.02243918366730213,-0.021107623353600502,-0.019758816808462143,0.05088771507143974,0.10369271785020828,0.058859750628471375,0.0048711770214140415,0.030834343284368515,0.013979491777718067,-0.001031846972182393,-0.039232414215803146,0.009992784820497036,-0.027045557275414467,0.02573697827756405,-0.0023174360394477844,0.05687079206109047,0.06616121530532837,0.0139273377135396,0.023598702624440193,0.01038082130253315,0.018008405342698097,0.06112073361873627,0.05007384344935417,0.044652655720710754,0.03693944960832596,0.03153499215841293,0.035245925188064575,0.010289320722222328,-0.030131498351693153,0.01778731867671013,0.02661830186843872,-0.011766329407691956,0.025287490338087082,0.018395138904452324,0.013796616345643997,-0.005250705871731043,0.004199165850877762,0.03873872384428978,0.020999450236558914,0.009238230995833874,-0.071991927921772,0.025937573984265327,-0.009867