(485, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1763322710800.mp3', 'compressed_1763322710800.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1763322710800.mp4', 'My name is Khushboo Kumani. I am MBA student specializing in marketing. I would identify myself as someone who is curious about people and how do they make decisions. That curiosity pushed me towards marketing in the first place. I interned at GFS Sheet. The project was about using weather data for agriculture and risk management and it was about using AI and ML to forecast windfall. That raw data helped me how data can be used in real life. I got to know the basics of AI and ML and gained exposure to python. I secured 7th rank in BBA at Macro University. My key skills are digital marketing, consumer behavior and marketing research. Thank you.', 349, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1763322710800.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1763322710800.jpg', '2025-11-17 01:23:56.728051', 'J007', 'null', 'null', '[0.01704104244709015,-0.0038719498552381992,-0.015207563526928425,0.0499098114669323,0.10689574480056763,0.0556141696870327,0.010787867940962315,0.035458456724882126,0.02393363043665886,0.01392916589975357,-0.03475641459226608,0.02691434510052204,-0.027268867939710617,0.026343615725636482,-0.013894257135689259,0.05556119605898857,0.06874702870845795,0.019352668896317482,0.02478298358619213,0.01785764843225479,-0.0034598305355757475,0.06507085263729095,0.042262692004442215,0.041380625218153,0.04076046124100685,0.011393037624657154,0.025995885953307152,0.004196106921881437,-0.03364139795303345,0.021405687555670738,0.030866963788866997,-0.009984493255615234,0.018744096159934998,0.020082801580429077,0.013111347332596779,-0.009395820088684559,0.0064460826106369495,0.03731812164187431,0.001932261511683464,0.010318455286324024,-0.06943139433860779,0.031161503866314888,-0.008826721459627151,0.002147132297977805,-0.05640539154410362,-0.002776145935