(486, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1763325417185.mp3', 'compressed_1763325417185.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1763325417185.mp4', 'Hello, I\'m Aryan Verma, a second year MBA student at IFMR gsb, and I would like to express my interest in this role through my learnings from my MBA Academy journey as well as from my summer internship. So I\'ve undertaken a lot of academic projects in which I\'ve analyzed industries, sectors and companies and learned about two things. First is that companies need to maintain healthy financials to get through hurdles, and also they need a perfectly tailored marketing strategy, which they would require to grow their business as well as to penetrate the relevant market. From a summer internship, I have learned about translating business and client needs into actionable insights. At the same time, I\'ve also learned that not all the stakeholders will have the relevant domain knowledge, but through collaborative effort we can fill in those gaps. So that was about me. Thank you for your time.', 326, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1763325417185.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1763325417185.jpg', '2025-11-17 02:09:13.352727', 'J007', 'null', 'null', '[0.032746799290180206,-0.005194810684770346,-0.005669602658599615,0.039915766566991806,0.10184402763843536,0.03779112175107002,0.019678842276334763,0.027771741151809692,0.025297097861766815,0.003634980646893382,-0.03431679308414459,0.012537323869764805,-0.023389451205730438,0.025095822289586067,-0.008078917860984802,0.05169694498181343,0.06420575082302094,0.011222978122532368,0.026497183367609978,0.002450676867738366,0.009291276335716248,0.07914770394563675,0.05489301308989525,0.05240441486239433,0.04786277934908867,0.015785017982125282,0.037604980170726776,0.019502056762576103,-0.03540165722370148,0.0023043472319841385,0.029674382880330086,-0.024248404428362846,0.015428593382239342,0.019098233