(487, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1763328000962.mp3', 'compressed_1763328000962.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1763328000962.mp4', 'Hello, I\'m Manisha and I\'m pursuing MBA at IFMR Graduate School of Business. I\'m naturally gravitated to the roles that forced me to think analytically and work under pressure. During my internship at Bajaj Capital Limited which is a financial services company, my key role was to acquire customer and help them to make their investment decision based on their risk appetite and the goal of their investment. So basically it was working with people and I enjoyed it as much as I enjoy working with numbers. And on the technical side, I have done projects in valuation for the CIPLA limited and also build a modeling for the option strategy using volatility. Apart from academics, I take responsibilities very seriously, whether it is being representative for my class and whether it\'s volunteering for any social cause. I.', 371, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1763328000962.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1763328000962.jpg', '2025-11-17 02:53:04.380135', 'J007', 'null', 'null', '[0.02483958564698696,-0.01395065151154995,-0.020635275170207024,0.036423731595277786,0.10866650938987732,0.07404768466949463,0.0020912932232022285,0.034079790115356445,0.008446881547570229,0.01021552924066782,-0.01258002407848835,0.011353343725204468,-0.027068473398685455,0.025019081309437752,0.004206823650747538,0.04985637217760086,0.06564254313707352,0.007893422618508339,0.007915440015494823,-0.0032161446288228035,0.02068358287215233,0.07246757298707962,0.057441625744104385,0.03436052426695824,0.03741498664021492,0.027221018448472023,0.04102536290884018,0.014463212341070175,-0.01664815843105316,0.006269008852541447,0.028361082077026367,-0.022387035191059113,0.016434025019407272,0.024928810074925423,0.026358025148510933,-0.01371933426707983,0.011937220580875874,0.038