(505, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1763360319286.mp3', 'compressed_1763360319286.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1763360319286.mp4', 'Hi, my name is Divim Kungar and I\'m currently pursuing MBA from IFMR gsp. I introduce myself as someone who brings structure and calm energy into fast moving situations. In my internship at Perfective and Malay I remember walking into a project where the data was scattered and the deadline was tight. So I divided the entire data set into five individual pieces and started working on it weekly. That moment reinforced how much I enjoy taking ownership when things look messy. A similar pattern showed up during one of our academic projects. We had to work on campaigning online for Chennai on different social media platforms. There was a lot to do and that deadline was again short. So I initiated a short regroup, assigned the responsibilities based on everyone\'s strength. This helped us in not only completing the project smoothly but also being recognized among the top entries. Apart from my cats, I have worked as a class rep which helped me build consistency and discipline some something I bring into every task. Thank you.', 366, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1763360319286.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1763360319286.jpg', '2025-11-17 11:49:36.555772', 'J007', '', 'null', '[0.03550521656870842,-0.0017195199616253376,-0.00782018806785345,0.04704584553837776,0.09166346490383148,0.05098980665206909,0.011728836223483086,0.02421828918159008,0.01712985523045063,0.00589717598631978,-0.03686418756842613,0.0092388316988945,-0.03320765495300293,0.009496603161096573,-0.013046062551438808,0.04879027605056763,0.05749758332967758,0.007419093977659941,0.020728126168251038,0.004834244959056377,0.012474077753722668,0.06469231843948364,0.04592355713248253,0.04547523707151413,0.05040843412280083,0.032762978225946426,0.04610354080796242,0.008826196193695