(506, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1763360694509.mp3', 'compressed_1763360694509.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1763360694509.mp4', 'Hi, my name is Inish and I am from Delhi. Currently I am pursuing my MBA in Finance from Ifama gsb. Before this I completed my BBA which ignited my interest in finance and I decided to pursue it further. During BBA days I interned at the Leading Solution Private Limited in sales, marketing and HR department where I learned the basics of HR and developed a marketing campaign to boost sales. My latest internship was with GFST where I worked on weather intelligence. For agriculture I worked on geospatial data and built rainfall forecasting models. This internship told me how data can be crucial for the real time update for the farmers and help policymakers. Both my internships and my academic projects make me ready for the future ready make me ready for future and makes me a problem solver.', 376, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1763360694509.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1763360694509.jpg', '2025-11-17 11:56:04.914994', 'J007', 'null', 'null', '[0.024127330631017685,-0.025245141237974167,-0.011071320623159409,0.03303936496376991,0.10086570680141449,0.06363561749458313,0.0023611802607774734,0.02696741186082363,0.011524210684001446,0.011824116110801697,-0.037313733249902725,0.004838442429900169,-0.02745220623910427,0.016922101378440857,0.003592952387407422,0.05547906830906868,0.07283823937177658,0.016886189579963684,0.021717797964811325,0.0031428083311766386,0.015593057498335838,0.07321059703826904,0.042634449899196625,0.04296785593032837,0.04832598194479942,0.03510010242462158,0.02905108593404293,0.023210547864437103,-0.03891339153051376,0.022011814638972282,0.02792366035282612,-0.020606372505426407,0.019274087622761726,0.016415370628237724,0.012465216219425201,-0.012049642391502857,0.015811368823051453,0.037320829927921295,0.0068092588