(507, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1763360614807.mp3', 'compressed_1763360614807.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1763360614807.mp4', 'Hello, my name is Shruti and I come from Nagpur, Maharashtra. I did my BBA there and currently I\'m pursuing MBA in Marketing at IFMS JSP Kriya University. Over the last year, I have taken various marketing courses and each one of it has shaped how I really think. Each one offered something different, whether it\'s understanding consumer psychology, building a brand story, or using data to make smarter decisions. And I got to put all of this into practice. During my internship at Kabutta, I worked on B2B, outreach, lead generation, and crafting brand communication. And that\'s when I realized something important that people do don\'t respond to the best pitch. They respond to a person who genuinely listens. And when I started focusing on understanding what buyers actually wanted, the conversations became easier and the pipeline became stronger. That\'s why I enjoy marketing and client relationship management so much. Thank you.', 317, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1763360614807.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1763360614807.jpg', '2025-11-17 11:56:21.131596', 'J007', '', 'null', '[0.024272331967949867,1.0088996350532398E-4,-0.00788532942533493,0.040258459746837616,0.08734073489904404,0.06275884062051773,0.007721281144768,0.04239383339881897,0.03632250055670738,0.014515573158860207,-0.026839327067136765,0.018899841234087944,-0.030728407204151154,0.019642140716314316,-0.0027536016423255205,0.04822719097137451,0.06983307749032974,0.026057835668325424,0.009669458493590355,0.010831356979906559,0.010856236331164837,0.07428682595491409,0.04143640026450157,0.05127036198973656,0.056777890771627426,0.013299246318638325,0.04112476110458374,0.014216665178537369,-0.0394163578748703,0.02456621080636978,0.02738029509782791,-0.02245309390127659,0.015