(514, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1763403640637.mp3', 'compressed_1763403640637.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1763403640637.mp4', 'Hi, I\'m Sameer Ahmed, an electrical engineer by training and pursuing an MBA in finance. Although I come from the capital city of New Delhi, but moving through seven different academic institutions has shaped me into an adaptable person who thrives in a diverse environment. This was put to test when I was first introduced to the corporate world during my internship at SBI Caps in the Debt Capital Market division, I was assigned to research upon sustainable and sustainability link bonds. I also designed investor presentations and made cash flow models using Excel for the coupon payments. At present, I\'m drawn to finance because of the decision making involved in it, which is backed by the number crunching. All my learnings have been stepping stones to my team\'s success in various competitions ranging from finance all the way to public speed. Last but not the least, I am an active member of the Cultural Committee of ifmr, which sides with my extrovert nature.', 382, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1763403640637.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1763403640637.jpg', '2025-11-17 23:52:00.313709', 'J007', 'null', 'null', '[0.023335712030529976,-0.020124131813645363,-0.005186673253774643,0.04414532706141472,0.0912962332367897,0.05036802962422371,-0.0105745829641819,0.0470825619995594,3.232021408621222E-4,0.004011194221675396,-0.0326383039355278,0.022372683510184288,-0.043506987392902374,0.01727576181292534,-0.012525921687483788,0.053863752633333206,0.06476138532161713,0.013944080099463463,0.001383899594657123,-0.006787767633795738,0.027163079008460045,0.08835674077272415,0.0677056610584259,0.05682476982474327,0.04820889234542847,0.030226057395339012,0.027134496718645096,-0.004756446927785873,-0.03161560744047165,0.011350591666996479,0.035312