(516, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1764658208234.mp3', 'compressed_1764658208234.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1764658208234.mp4', 'Hi, my name is Siddhi Arora. I turn ambiguity into clarity, problems into product, and ideas into impact. I\'m an MBA student with a design background. I bring with myself around two years of work experience in business development, strategy and product management, having a skill set of collaboration, time management, strategy, data driven decision making and product acumen. Working as a product manager, I learned what it takes to wear multiple hats, to drive your product to excellence and to be the face of the brand, the representative of the brand. My experience working across geographies, working with varied team cultures and learning new languages has shaped me to someone who thrives in diverse environments and learns quickly with all that I have to offer. With my curiosity, my skill set and my experience, I\'m excited to make a lasting impact at your organization, cavancare. Thank you.', 332, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1764658208234.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1764658208234.jpg', '2025-12-02 12:21:24.351273', 'J008', 'null', 'null', '[0.032709743827581406,0.023460129275918007,-0.017741374671459198,0.04241788014769554,0.09301511943340302,0.060960378497838974,0.01144650112837553,0.04068448394536972,0.03752947226166725,-0.0014509782195091248,-0.033018700778484344,0.005621170159429312,-0.03788687661290169,0.02103477716445923,-0.01829640381038189,0.06562508642673492,0.06287869065999985,0.03233105689287186,0.021471187472343445,0.01276073232293129,0.006255910731852055,0.0583161823451519,0.033848896622657776,0.04893377423286438,0.04465862363576889,0.028564993292093277,0.04110163822770119,0.008778301998972893,-0.03197737783193588,0.019105153158307076,0.03131145238876343,-0.026270141825079918,0.026686443015933037,-0.007225981913506