(517, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1764676223091.mp3', 'compressed_1764676223091.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1764676223091.mp4', 'Hi, I am Tushar, currently pursuing my MBA with a strong background in the field of sales and marketing. Now what would I like to tell about myself is I love understanding consumers and turning those insights into ideas that helps the brand grow. Throughout my work at prplguru and Jaipur Rucks, I have built some solid skills in the field of digital marketing, market research and strategic communications. At propelguru, I learned how to use data to improve targeting and campaign performance. At Jaipur, I had the opportunity to study international consumers and created content that matched their preferences. What sets me apart is my ability to blend technical thinking with creative execution. I am someone who learns quickly, adapts easily, and enjoys solving real marketing challenges. Cavancare\'s innovative and consumer first approach really aligns with my strengths and I am excited for the opportunity to contribute fresh ideas and deliver meaningful impact. Thank you.', 372, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1764676223091.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1764676223091.jpg', '2025-12-02 17:22:22.866108', 'J008', 'null', 'null', '[0.03832058608531952,-0.00820065476000309,-0.003071521408855915,0.044806335121393204,0.09179312735795975,0.0576961487531662,0.005708808545023203,0.04272971674799919,0.03704360872507095,-6.898557185195386E-4,-0.030857760459184647,0.014188735745847225,-0.02224969118833542,0.028773773461580276,9.201861685141921E-4,0.06306666880846024,0.06679178774356842,0.027376333251595497,0.014733167365193367,0.008401100523769855,0.003221950028091669,0.049409959465265274,0.03764178603887558,0.043475259095430374,0.04194732755422592,0.013226105831563473,0.04064454883337021,0.019214211031794548,-0.043039556592702866,0.01016428694128990