(518, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1764686259026.mp3', 'compressed_1764686259026.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1764686259026.mp4', 'Hello, I am Brindha and I am from Chennai and currently pursuing MBA at IFMR Graduate School of Business. I did my summer internship at Reserve bank of India. Before joining MBA. I had 14 months of experience in assisting in my family business as a storekeeper where I was responsible for recording sales and inventory and I also coordinated among various customer clients and suppliers while managing day to day operations. I did my undergrad in Computer Science and engineering at RMK College of Engineering and Technology. During my first year I worked on analyzing McDonald\'s global marketing and growth strategies using various marketing framework which helped me to understand brand positioning and consumer driven decision making. I also worked on market research project on WPL where as a team we conducted various qualitative and quantitative analysis to understand consumer perception and translated these findings into insights. I am fluent in English and I can also converse in Tamil and Telugu. Thank you.', 386, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1764686259026.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1764686259026.jpg', '2025-12-02 20:11:52.032703', 'J008', '', 'null', '[0.025052113458514214,-0.001645915792323649,-0.004823558032512665,0.029075950384140015,0.10610885918140411,0.07200384140014648,0.006851478014141321,0.02795417606830597,0.011882088147103786,0.015010972507297993,-0.031383100897073746,0.019220391288399696,-0.021086465567350388,0.01957378350198269,-0.004473889712244272,0.05578285828232765,0.07142362743616104,0.018823018297553062,0.01977478340268135,8.827975252643228E-4,0.014690202660858631,0.07008446007966995,0.06316056102514267,0.04200572520494461,0.03947054594755173,0.030499514192342758,0.03927263617515564,0.01705125905573368,-0.03689