(519, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/audio/1764689762285.mp3', 'compressed_1764689762285.mp4', '/home/wezume/htdocs/wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1764689762285.mp4', 'I am Ananya Parthasati. I see myself as someone who\'s curious to know more on consumer behavior. One such project which I worked on was understanding driver and passenger patterns at Stop Signals, which helped me identify behavioral patterns which could guide decisions. And I also had done a live project at Grant Thornton Bharat where I had interacted with Kirana store owners, understanding the pain points as to how quick commerce affects their business. Apart from this, I had also digitally marketed Bangalore as a city, which helped me understand how branding works. And finally, my internship at Sony, where I had had to interview employees, helped me empathize, analyze, and give actionable insights. All these helped me shape into someone who could get real consumer insights and convert it into brand building.', 344, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/compressed_1764689762285.mp4', NULL, 'https://wezume.in/uploads/videos/thumbnails/thumbnail_compressed_1764689762285.jpg', '2025-12-02 21:07:06.186848', 'J008', 'null', 'null', '[0.03251589834690094,-0.008260685950517654,-0.011082462035119534,0.04219362884759903,0.09549812972545624,0.06158404424786568,0.011173169128596783,0.03267744556069374,0.03706466034054756,0.002732089953497052,-0.02953452616930008,0.01737484522163868,-0.03254246339201927,0.023982742801308632,-0.012142476625740528,0.050196465104818344,0.07045966386795044,0.022970737889409065,0.017935482785105705,0.007989857345819473,0.011842407286167145,0.06988228112459183,0.04655138775706291,0.053342390805482864,0.04374534264206886,0.014136594720184803,0.02598842978477478,0.007421767804771662,-0.03306146711111069,0.023471632972359657,0.028472909703850746,-0.02013230510056019,0.01799618825316429,0.009071089327335358,0.023924389854073524,-0.006073674187064171,0.01300787553191185,0.038208302110